playlists.title: One-Punch Man (Season 3) [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Saitama is a hero who only became a hero for fun.
After three years of "special training," he’s become so strong that he's practically invincible. In fact, he's too strong—even his mightiest opponents are taken out with a single punch. Alongside Genos, his faithful disciple, Saitama performs his official hero duties as a member of the Hero Association.
One day, monsters claiming to be from the Monster Association suddenly appeared, taking a child of Hero Association executive hostage. The S-class heroes gather and plan a raid on the Monster Association hideout to rescue the hostage. Meanwhile, Garou, a "human monster" who was taken by the Monster Association during a battle with the heroes, awakens in the Monster Association hideout.

playlists.title: SPY×FAMILY Season 3 [English Sub]
playlists.description:
In an era in which the nations of the world were waging a fierce war of information, Ostania and Westalis had been in a cold war state for decades. 
Twilight is one of the best spies from Westalis and he has been charged with the top-secret mission to keep his eye on Desmond, a key figure from Ostania who is threatening the peace between the East and the West.
His mission is to "Establish a family and infiltrate the social circle at the prestigious school his target's son attends.
However, the daughter Twilight meets is a telepath who can read people's minds and his wife is an assassin! 
The peace of the world rests in the hands of a family of three hiding their true identities from each other.

playlists.title: Unlimited Gacha [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Anime Full Title: 《Backstabbed in a Backwater Dungeon: My Trusted Companions Tried to Kill Me, but Thanks to the Gift of an Unlimited Gacha I Got LVL 9999 Friends and Am Out for Revenge on My Former Party Members and the World》

The Goddess once created nine races. Among them, the weakest and most ridiculed were the humans. Light, a young human boy, was fortunate to be welcomed into the Concord of the Tribes, a party made up of nine races. For a time, he was happy. However, it was all a fleeting illusion. What awaited him was betrayal in the world's largest and deadliest dungeon, the Abyss. Light manages to survive, and at the bottom of the Abyss, he discovers the true power of his gift of Infinite Gacha. Crawling back from the depths of despair, Light goes on to build the mightiest kingdom. With his unique gift of Infinite Gacha in hand, the curtain rises on a tale of revenge that will shake the world!!

playlists.title: A Gatherer's Adventure in Isekai
playlists.description: Takeru Kamishiro is just a regular office worker. However, when he wished for a slightly different day, he was reincarnated into a world of sword and magic! He is also gifted with physical enhancement, incredible mana, and the "Search" ability that allows him to see the value of the materials he found! And so, Takeru begins his second life gathering materials. Surrounded by the unique but lively friends of an ancient dragon cub, a mischievous elf, a lizardman warrior, and a beautiful divine horse, Takeru's trip in another world has begun!

He conceals his existence to uncover the king's schemes, only to be falsely accused of a crime he did not commit and driven into exile.He swears vengeance against the king and escapes into the unexplored depths of the Great Labyrinth of Kantinen, where he encounters the elf girl Amelia Rosequartz.The curtain rises on the tale of a boy granted the power of an Assassin and his journey with an elf girl toward becoming the Silent Assassin.

Allen's unconventional lesson that defies common sense gently illuminates the girl's future.

Killed by a stalker, when he wakes up he reincarnated as a goblin named Gobrou.
He evolves abnormally with his "Absorption" ability, which makes him stronger the more he devours, and in the blink of an eye he becomes the leader of the goblin community...
In a different world where the strong preying on the weak, Gobrou and his talented friends are surviving as underdogs!
A monster reincarnation fantasy has started!

playlists.title: I'm the Evil Lord of an Intergalactic Empire! [English Sub]
playlists.description: "I'll become an evil lord and do as I please!"Liam is a reincarnator who became the head of the family at a young age. He was born into a count's household that governs the frontier of an interstellar nation, the Algrand Empire.Reflecting on his previous life, where his kindness led to constant loss, he now resolves to live as an evil lord, the one who takes from others and oppresses his people!"Since it's a sci-fi world, I want to pilot robots!""I want to master the strongest swordsmanship and act as recklessly as I please!""Eventually, I dream of building a harem and indulging in a life of luxury!"However...Even though Liam thinks he's acting like an evil lord, for some reason, his people are grateful, and his popularity keeps rising!Set in an interstellar nation filled with magic and robots, a misunderstanding tale of territory management on a super-galactic scale begins!

playlists.description: Ein is an Appraiser, a job that is considered the weakest and most underprivileged, whose only skill is Appraisal. His peers treated him horribly, ridiculed and called him a "rubbish picker". Unable to like himself, he spent his days in self-loathing.His destiny then takes a drastic turn when he meets Yuri, a spirit of Yggdrasil, as well as Ursula, Yuri's guardian.As Yuri gives Ein the Spirit Eye, he undergoes rigorous training under Ursula to master its power. As Ein grows stronger, he embarks on a journey to fulfill Yuri's wish to meet the other sisters of Yggdrasil.With his inherent kindness and newfound courage, Ein overcomes numerous challenges on his path.

playlists.title: From Bureaucrat to Villainess: Dad's Been Reincarnated! [English Sub]
playlists.description: Kenzaburo Tondabayashi, a 52-year-old diligent public employee, died after a traffic incident… Or that was what's supposed to happen. When he wakes up, he finds himself reincarnated as a character from the world of the Otome game that his daughter loves, "Magical Academy Love & Beast". He is reincarnated as Grace Auvergne, the villainess who obstructs the love life of the game's protagonist, Anna Doll. And so, Grace Kenzaburo tries to act like a villainess just like how the original Grace was. However, due to his life experience, he views Anna through the eyes of a parent and gives her advice. Along with his "Elegant Cheat" which translates his plebeian manner into something elegant, he inadvertently raises his popularity and raises the flags of the capture targets. The weapon you need to survive in another world is not swords or magic, but the Old Man Skill that one has cultivated through living in society!

Hoping for their engagement to be called off, Leticia witnesses Prince Clarke escorting a mysterious woman at a ball one day. Her heart leaps at the thought of the prince changing his mind, but... Clarke isn't ready to give up on marriage! Leticia wants to escape her princess lessons and live freely. Determined to chase after her, Prince Clarke expresses his sincere affection. Thus begins a chaotic and heartwarming battle between a princess candidate who wants to break off the engagement and a prince who wants to marry her!

playlists.title: I Left my A-Rank Party to Help My Former Students Reach the Dungeon Depths! [English Sub]
playlists.description: "I quit!" Boldly declares the Red Mage Yuke as he walks away from Thunder Pike, an A-Rank party he has been part of for five years. Unable to endure being underestimated—no, outright ridiculed—by the other members, he finally abandons his prestigious position. While searching for a new party, Yuke reunites with three of his former students—Marina, Silk, and Rain—and joins their group. Encouraged by the girls who still admire him as their teacher, Yuke unleashes his unparalleled magical prowess and skills. By drawing out the best in his teammates, he leads them to triumph after triumph in their quests. With the help of the broadcasting artifact Camerat, Clover begins live streaming their adventures, steadily building a reputation that spreads across the land. Their ultimate dream? To conquer the most formidable labyrinth of all: The Colorless Abyss. But as they tackle dungeon after dungeon in pursuit of their goal, they find themselves gradually drawn into a maelstrom of chaos that threatens to upend the world itself—

playlists.title: Beheneko: The Elf-Girl’s Cat is Secretly an S-Ranked Monster! [English Sub]
playlists.description: Ruine, the city of Labyrinthos, where monsters run rampant within a maze-like dungeon, is home to countless adventurers.The protagonist, who lost his life and was reincarnated, wakes up inside the dungeon. And instead of a human, he looks just like a kitten!? But his true identity is that of an S-rank disaster-class monster... He's turned into a baby Behemoth!He encounters Aria, a novice D-rank adventurer. Mistaking him for a kitten, Aria takes the severely injured protagonist back with her to treat his wounds. She names him "Tama" and keeps him as her pet. Touched by her kindness, Tama vows to become Aria's knight and protector.Utilizing his S-rank abilities, Tama explores the dungeon alongside Aria. He'll meet a variety of unique companions, and sometimes be the subject of way too much cuddling, as his days as a knight (pet) begin!

Now united, Emilia's faction enjoys peaceful and fulfilling days while preparing for the Royal Selection. They accept and head for Priestella, where they soon encounter several reunions—one unexpected, one coincidental, and one fated.As evil stirs and unprecedented crises loom beneath the surface, Subaru Natsuki is about to confront yet another harsh fate.

playlists.title: The Most Notorious “Talker” Runs the World’s Greatest Clan [English Sub]
playlists.description:
A hero known as "Over Death" has a grandson named Noel. Noel admires his grandfather and aspires to become the strongest Seeker. However, the job he possesses is classified as the weakest support role, "Talker". Despite inheriting his grandfather's will and putting in extraordinary effort to become a powerful explorer, Noel could not bridge the gap created by his natural talent.
Nevertheless, he uncovers a path to becoming the strongest through his rare and exceptional cunning. By gathering companions, creating the strongest clan, and becoming its master, he aims to outwit enemies and lead his team to unprecedented heights. The most fearsome "Talker" paves the way to becoming the strongest, using any means necessary.

playlists.description: "Let's be Treasure Hunters! We have only one goal: to become the strongest heroes in the world."Among the six people who have made that vow, only one young man is particularly untalented.One day, as he expresses his frustration, his childhood friend says to him.""Krai, you don't have any role in particular, so why not become our leader?""The ""Grieving Soul"" party, formed by the extremely talented monsters (childhood friends), has made a name for themselves throughout the Imperial capital within a few years, and Krai, being the top of a party, is promoted to the top of the strongest party.Due to the high expectations of those around him, his words and actions are often misunderstood, and the situation takes an unexpected turn...This is the heroic tale of Krai Andrey, filled with glory and pain, the leader of the strongest party, known as the strongest Clan Master!

playlists.title: A Journey Through Another World: Raising Kids While Adventuring [English Sub]
playlists.description: 【Synopsis】Due to a God's mistake, Takumi Kayano lost his life and was reincarnated. He received various skills and was sent to another world, where he found himself in the middle of a dangerous forest teeming with monsters.In that forest, Takumi found a boy and a girl who appeared to be twins. He named them Alan and Elena and took them into his custody. Despite being shocked at how easily the twins beat the monsters with their fighting skills, Takumi made it to town and to make a living he registered to the adventurer's guild.Now his life of leisurely living as an adventurer while looking after Alan and Elena growing up had just begun.【Staff】Original Story: Shizuru Minazuki (published by AlphaPolis)Original Illustration: YamakawaManga: Tomomi MizunaDirector: Atsushi NigorikawaSeries Composition: Jun MaekawaCharacter Design: Yuki NakanoDirector of Art: Satoru KuwaharaColor Design: Mika IwamiDirectors of Photography: Nozomi ShitaraSound Director: Hiroto MorishitaSound Effect: Yoko SakuraiSound Recording: Masato MutoSound Recording Assistant: Risako YamadaSound Studio: Three S StudioSound Production: Ai AddictionMusic: Akiya SuzukiEditing: Motoki Niimi (REAL-T)Production Studio: EMT SquaredProduction Cooperation: B-BirdProduced by: GencoOpening Theme: "Yururing Travel Days" by Tebasaki Sensation (Dreamusic)Ending Theme: "MAKUAKE" by Gohobi (Pony Canyon)

playlists.description: 【Synopsis】At school, the aloof high school student, Touka Mimori, is summoned to another world as a hero along with his classmates. While the goddess Vysis identifies his classmates one after another with S-rank and A-rank abilities, Touka is declared to be the lowest rank, E-rank, and marked for "disposal." Abandoned in ruins with a zero survival rate, Touka, dismissed as a failure, attempts to escape using his "abnormal status skills." playlists.title: I PARRY EVERYTHING [English Sub]
playlists.description: 【Synopsis】After traveling the world, battling monsters, and protecting the innocent, aspiring adventurer Noor faced a bitter truth: he possessed zero talent for adventuring. Nevertheless, young Noor pressed on with unyielding determination. He devoted a decade to refining the weakest skill, [Parry], mastering it to the point of deflecting a thousand swords. And yet he realized that his efforts were futile—he could never become an adventurer with only low-level skills, resigning himself to doing odd jobs in town. Little did he know, he was already among the world's strongest. One fateful day, Noor's destiny takes an unforeseen twist when he inadvertently rescues Princess Lynne from a monster attack. ──This is the story of how an invincible yet humble man, oblivious to his own strength, masters the weakest skill [Parry] and uses it to defeat powerful foes.【Staff】Original Creator: Nabeshiki (Earth Star Novel, published by Earth Star Entertainment)Original Illustrator: KawaguchiManga: KRSGDirector: Dai FukuyamaSeries Composition: Shigeru MurakoshiCharacter Design: Chikako NomaSub-character Design: Toshiaki OhashiProp Design: Haruna HashimotoMonster Design: Hiroyasu Oda (Studio Mogana)Main Animator: Satoshi HorisawaArt Director/Art Setting: Mikihiro HarabeColor Design: Nanako OkazakiDirector of Photography: Shingo Fukuyo (J.C.STAFF)Editor: Go TsuyoshiSound Director: Ryo TanakaMusic: Tatsuhiko Saiki, BeauDamianAnimation Production: OLM

"If you want to chase after your dream, then you better do it while you're still young." Everybody thinks that way. But sometimes, some adults will never give up. playlists.title: Date A Live V [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Spirits have the appearance of human girls, but they are different from humans.
They are even called the nemeses of mankind because of their powerful ability to cause disasters dubbed "spatial quakes" when they emerge from another dimension.
The only means that mankind has of dealing with the threat of these Spirits is to exterminate them by military force, or...

Date them and make them succumb to the power of love!

Shido Itsuka has the ability to seal the power of a Spirit by making her fall for him and kissing her.
He has been saving mankind and Spirits with his power, but a great upheaval is about to happen to him.
DEM Industry, one of the world's largest corporations specializing in Realizer, is after the power of the Spirits and attacks with all its might to take away Shido's life.
Then, a mysterious girl from the depths of Shido's memory reveals herself.
The biggest battle in the history, with so many agendas intertwined, shall begin.

playlists.description:
▶️ 《That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime》 
🔥 Full Series Playlist： 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLwLSw1_eDZl3_YNRvXA7O89pNPsj1WIkb  
.

Rimuru had officially become a Demon Lord after defeating Clayman. With the end of Walpurgis, Rimuru's territory now extended to the entirety of the Great Forest of Jura. With more residents at their hands as a result, Rimuru decided to hold a Founder's Festival to celebrate his becoming a Demon Lord and to greet all the representatives of other races coming to see him. Meanwhile, in the Holy Empire of Lubelius, the home ground of the anti-monster religion, Luminous Faith, Hinata, the Captain of the Crusaders, received a letter from Rimuru. However, it was a declaration of war that had been falsified by someone.

With Hinata reportedly heading to Tempest, what decision will Rimuru make?

Rimuru's new challenge in his pursuit of a prosperous, peaceful relationship between humans and monsters, where he must discern the true enemies and allies, begins.

playlists.title: Jellyfish Can't Swim in the Night [English Sub]
playlists.description:
"I" want to shine like a "somebody" too.

Trends dictate everything, from what people talk about tomorrow to what clothes they buy this week.
In this busy world, people don't have the leeway to even dream about being a "somebody."

Yoru Umitsuki, an illustrator on indefinite hiatus
Nonoka Tachibana, an ex-idol looking to prove herself through her songs
Nox Ryugasaki, a self-proclaimed strongest Vtuber
Kimura-chan, a mysterious composer who wants to support her idol

Four girls who stick out a bit from the rest of the world band together to form the anonymous artist "JELEE."

If it's JELEE and not themselves, they might have what it takes to shine.

playlists.title: THE NEW GATE [English Sub]
playlists.description:
The online game "The New Gate" was a virtual space crowded with many players, but one day it became something far more sinister, trapping the players inside the game and tormenting them.
Shin, the man known as the game's strongest player, stood up to the fight and defeated the game world's strongest enemy, Origin. After Origin's defeat, a resounding announcement says that the game has been cleared and all the trapped players will be released.
As players are logging out, Shin is about to do the same, but a new door suddenly opens. After being enveloped in light, the world Shin opens his eyes to turns out to be the world of The New Gate 500 years after the game was cleared.

playlists.title: I Was Reincarnated as the 7th Prince so I Can Take My Time Perfecting My Magical Ability [English Sub]
playlists.description:
What's important in sorcery are "Lineage", "Aptitude", and "Dedication".
A "mediocre" sorcerer who deeply loved sorcery yet was not blessed with lineage or aptitude had died a tragic death. On the verge of death, he wished he could have learned more sorcery and perfected it. He found himself reincarnated into Llyod, the 7th prince of the Kingdom of Saloum, who has a strong bloodline of sorcery.

Reborn with the perfect bloodline and aptitude, having his memories intact made what he could not achieve in his past life etched strongly within him, and he enjoys the unrivaled life of "mastering sorcery all he wants" using his excessive mana!

The manga serial based on the light novel released in the manga app "Magazine Pocket" from Kodansha has ranked number one in the sales ranking with more than 3 million copies printed! Now the most hyped "reincarnation fantasy" title is being adapted into anime!

The story takes place in a world inhabited by monsters and demons. In this story, the main character Llyod possesses mana so immense that anyone who is familliar with sorcery fears him. The story follows his growth as he studies sorcery as he pleases and strives to master it. Although a bit light-hearted, the story is packed with exhilarating and vigorous magical battles with overwhelming power!
Here begins the carefree reincarnation story of the 7th Prince!

playlists.title: Chillin' in Another World with Level 2 Super Cheat Powers [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Banaza lives his life working as an ordinary merchant. One day, he gets summoned to the Magical Kingdom of Klyrode as a Hero Candidate. However, because his Level 1 abilities are the same as those of an average citizen, he is branded a failed hero and is unable to return home because of a mistake made by the kingdom.

Banaza is banished from the royal capital to the frontier. While trying to survive in the forest, he fights off slimes that attack him. Upon reaching Level 2, all his stats become the unfamiliar "∞" symbol.

This is the story of a man blessed with Transcendence who chose to change his name and appearance to live his life in a different world, a demon who fell in love with a member of the enemy race, and their tumultuous married life. They strive for a peaceful life as they rope in characters of all different races!

A monster reincarnation fantasy has started!

playlists.title: Chained Soldier [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Mysterious gates suddenly appear all over Japan.
In another dimension beyond the gate called Mato, there are Peaches that only women can eat giving them unique abilities. They are fighting as a female-organized fighting group, the "Demon Defense Force", in order to exterminate the monster known as "Shuuki".

One day, Yuuki Wakura, a high school boy who is looking for a place to play a role, happens to wander into Mato and is attacked by Shuukis. Kyouka Uzen, the beautiful commander of the Demon Defense Force 7th Squad, rushes to his aid. Yuuki is transformed into a slave by Kyouka's ability, and then he successfully defeats Shuukis. He ends up fighting Shuukis as a slave and the caretaker of the Demon Defense Force.

A battle fantasy of "the boy who becomes a pet" starts here!

playlists.title: The Wrong Way to Use Healing Magic [English Sub]
playlists.description: Ken Usato is an ordinary high school student. On his way home from school, he is swallowed up by a magic circle along with student council president Suzune Inukami and his classmate Kazuki Ryusen. The next thing they know, they find themselves in another world. The three of them were summoned as "heroes" to fight against the Demon Lord's army that's invading the kingdom. However, it turns out that only Suzune and Kazuki have what it takes to become heroes. Usato was just summoned by accident! The situation changes drastically when it is discovered that Usato has an aptitude for "healing magic." Rose, the leader of the Rescue Squad, appears and takes Usato away by force. What awaits Usato is a hellish training regimen beyond anything he could have ever imagined!

playlists.title: My Instant Death Ability is Overpowered [English Sub]
playlists.description:
It's the birth of the strongest protagonist who can kill all his enemies instantly!

During a school trip, Yogiri Takatou and his classmates were suddenly summoned to another world. The one who summoned them is a Sage named Sion. She gives them a special ability called "Gift", and unilaterally pronounces that they must complete the trials to become a Sage.

Even though they are all still shaken by the sudden situation, they begin to take action.

However, for some reason, some students cannot receive Gift, including Yogiri and Tomochika Dannoura. Those students without abilities are left as decoys when a dragon is approaching.

The remaining students are killed one after another by the dragon. yogiri and Tomochika are in danger!

...that was what we thought.

"Die."

Yogiri defeated the dragon with a single word. And what a surprise, he has an "Instant Death" ability, which allows him to instantly kill any target of his choice!

Yogiri and Tomochika begin a journey in order to get back to their original world. They meet various people from another world who have cheat-like abilities. An immortal vampire? A redo of a hero? A reincarnated person who is doted on by the gods? They are not a match against the Instant Death ability!

An adventure in another world of a downer boy with an unprecedented cheat ability as his weapon and a slightly clumsy pretty girl now begins!

playlists.title: Sasaki and Peeps [English Sub]
playlists.description:
A bird Sasaki bought from the pet shop was a reincarnated great renown sage from another world.

"My name is Piercarlo, an inhabitant of another world and a Starsage."

However, he's now a Java sparrow. Sasaki named his cute new pet "Peeps" and started living with him.

The sage then gave him the magic power to travel to another world. Every day returning from work, the two would enjoy a life in another world together! Eventually, the two start acting as merchants and selling the stuff from modern Japan to sell them in another world.

But then, one day, on his way back from work, Sasaki meets what's known as "Psychics." Sasaki survives the encounter using the magic power he got from Peeps. However, he gets mistaken as a psychic and is later scouted to join the national "Paranormal Phenomena Countermeasure Bureau."

Escape corporate slavery! Escape black company!
However, what he got was far from a stable public service job...

His meeting with a single Java sparrow greatly changed Sasaki's life! A story of another world fantasy x psychic battle set in both another world and modern Japan now begins!

playlists.title: Shangri-La Frontier [English Sub]
playlists.description:
What makes you game?

For every 100 amazing games, there are a thousand that are pure crap.
This is the story of Rakuro Hizutome, a man who loves, and is loved by, crappy video games,
and his journey in the world of Shangri-La Frontier, one of the greatest video games of all time.

The original web novel has over 500 million pageviews,
and is unique in that a manga adaptation was begun before the web novel story was released in print.
It also has the honor of being the first manga in Shonen Magazine’s sixty-plus years of history to win the quadruple reader survey crown!

Shangri-La Frontier takes gaming experiences that everyone can relate to and uses them to create an entirely new type of fantasy story.
It’s a story that will bring new adventure and excitement to both adults who can relive their old memories, and young people at the forefront of technology.

The ultimate “Game x Fantasy” story,
about a “crappy game hunter” who challenges one of the greatest games ever made!

playlists.title: Tearmoon Empire [English Sub]
playlists.description:
"My neck... It's here!? I... Became younger?!"
In a grand kingdom, Tearmoon Empire, Mia, a 20-year-old princess known as the "Selfish Princess", was executed by a guillotine when her people revolted.
That's how it was supposed to but when she woke up, she time leaped to her 12-year-old self!
It seems like this is a restarted world...
Under her pillow, there was a bloody diary that she wrote even moments before she got executed.
For the future of the Empire?
To save the people from famine?
For the sake of numerous soldiers who lost their lives in civil war?
That's not it! Everything is to avoid the route that leads to the guillotine!
"If it's only this much, it'll be a cinch when I put my back into it!"

The cowardly, self-preserving, super selfish, and useless princess, struggles hard for her own sake.
The movements made by the selfish princess bring miracles, and the fantasy story of changing history begins.

playlists.title: Frieren: Beyond Journey's End [English Sub]
playlists.description:
After ten long years of adventuring, the mage Frieren alongside the hero Himmel and his party members has defeated the Demon Lord and brought peace to the world.

As an elf that can live for more than a thousand years, Frieren went to travel alone, with a promise that she would reunite with Himmel and the others later on.

50 years later, Frieren visited Himmel. However, in contrast to her being no different from how she was 50 years ago, Himmel has aged a lot and doesn’t have long to live.

A short time later, after seeing Himmel passes away before her own eyes, she finally realizes that she has never made any effort to “understand people.”

With that regret, Frieren heads on a journey to “understand people.”
On her journey, she will meet with all kinds of people and deal with all kinds of things.

playlists.title: Berserk of Gluttony [English Sub]
playlists.description: In a world where skill is absolute, Fate, a boy despised for his incompetence, is forced to live at the bottom of the pile. This is because Fate's skill, "Gluttony," is completely useless, as it only makes him hungry. The Vlerick family, one of the highest-ranking families of holy knights in the world, picked him up, and he was subjected to violence and forced to do chores every day. The only relief is Roxy Hart who treats Fate without looking down on him, even though she is a holy knight. However, his world changes forever when he and Roxy accidentally kill a bandit that has entered the castle. The moment he took the enemy's life, his Gluttony skill was triggered and his opponent's power flowed into him. Fate's skill, "Gluttony," is an extraordinary skill that allows him to take away the skills and abilities of the person he kills. Fate has gained the power to fight, then meets Greed, a sword with an ego that also bears the name of a deadly sin and steps further into the world of conflict. In order to protect his loved ones and fight against the unreasonable world, Fate devours the enemies that stand in his way. The destiny of the boy who once simply grovelled on the ground begins to change rapidly.

playlists.title: Mushoku Tensei: Jobless Reincarnation Season 2 [English Sub]
playlists.description:
A 34-year-old man, jobless, shut-in and NEET.
On a certain day, after he got kicked out of the house, met his death in a traffic incident... or so the man thought.

The instant he thought that, suddenly he was reincarnated as "Rudeus" in a world of swords and magic. With the piled regret and experience from his previous life, he swears to live his life earnestly this time around.

Meeting with various peoples, various magic training... the now developed Rudeus is setting on a really harsh and cruel journey, such as Teleportation Incident involving his hometown, Fittoa Region, and other various tales.

After prevailing many hardships and successfully coming home, Rudeus became one with her beloved Eris.  However, the very next morning, Rudeus suffered a heavy shock after realising the sudden disappearance of Eris. He had given up on everything and reverted to his shut-in and NEET self, just like the previous world. Alas, as the only lost person in his family caused by Teleportation Incident, his mother, Zenith has not been found yet. Now he is determined to find Zenith, and Rudeus is standing up on his legs once more.

playlists.title: My Unique Skill Makes Me OP even at Level 1 [English Sub]
playlists.description:
The long-awaited Anime adaptation of the famous title that won 1st place in Shosetsuka ni Naro's daily, weekly, monthly, and quarterly ranking!
Ryota Sato, a salaryman who worked at a black company, one day found himself inside an unfamiliar dungeon! Turned out, he's now in a world where every single thing is monster drops.
With the help of the girl he met there, Emily, he checked his own status, only to learn that his stats are all "F" (weakest)! Not only that, his level is fixed at 1!
However, he later learns that he actually possesses an OP Unique Skill; "Drop Skill: ALL S"!!! With this, can Ryota survive living in this strange new world?!
The adventure of the strongest of the weak will now begin!

playlists.title: The Great Cleric: White-Collar Survival in Another World [English Sub]
playlists.description:
A former salaryman becomes undefeated in another world?!
A salaryman who was just a few steps away from getting his promotion got shot to his death.
For whatever reason, God decided to reincarnate the man as a 10-year-old Healer, Luciel, in another world.
Not only that, in this country he was born in, people seem to hate the Healers.
In fear for his safety, Luciel goes to the Adventurer Guild to earn the means to protect himself.
However, the training there was much more severe than he had imagined. On top of that, he had to drink a mysterious drink called "Substance X" every day.
Wait, how does this have anything to do with being a Healer?
The daily life survival of a masochistic zombie-like Healer now begins!

playlists.title: BanG Dream! It's MyGO!!!!! [English Sub]
playlists.description:
"Would you play in a band for your whole life?"

Late spring of the first year of high school.
Everyone at Haneoka Girls' High School is in a band. Anon, who enrolled in school late, rushes to find band members so she can fit in with her classmates as soon as possible. While at it, she learned that Tomori, the "Haneoka's Weirdo Girl", has not yet formed a band. And then, Anon calls on her...

The scream of our music may be covered in scars and ill-formed.
Even if we get lost, just move forward.

playlists.title: 放学后失眠的你 [中字]
playlists.description:
「只要曲在那里，我就想到学校去。我们这样算是什么关系。」

饱受失眠之苦的高中生中见丸太，为了摆脱文化祭的准备工作，走进变成仓库的天文台，在那里他遇见同样苦于失眠的曲伊咲。两个人因此有了共同的秘密基地……？

青春漫画的领头羊˙绪城真的原作，由年轻制作群将其动画化。

「你无法入睡的夜晚，必定有其意义存在」

playlists.title: Insomniacs after school [English Sub]
playlists.description:
"With Magari around, I feel like going to school now. I wonder what kind of relationship this is?"

A high school student, Ganta Nakami, who suffers from insomnia, meets Isaki Magari, who also suffers from insomnia, in an astronomical observatory, which is used as a storeroom now, when he's trying to skip helping out to prepare for the school's cultural festival. Thus, the two end up sharing a secret place...?

"Surely your sleepless nights must have some meanings to them..."

playlists.title: [Film] ARIA The AVVENIRE [English Sub]
playlists.description: Now that Akari Mizunashi is a Prima Undine and head of the Aria Company with her own apprentice, Ai Aino, she can't help but reminisce about her time as a Single. She has new responsibilities and much less time on her hands, but these changes bring with them new forms of miracles that Neo Venezia can give. Growing up into new roles is hard, but Akari can always count on the friends she's made on Aqua in times of need.

playlists.title: HUNTER×HUNTER 猎人 [中字]
playlists.description: 住在鲸鱼岛的少年-小杰，他的梦想就是要像父亲一样成为一名“猎人”。向分散在这个世界各角落的财宝、秘宝、珍品、珍兽…及“未知”赌上性命挑战，决心要成为全职猎人而踏上旅途的小杰，与同样以猎人为目标努力的酷拉皮卡、雷欧力、奇犽相遇。突破重重难关，终于通过猎人考试，而小杰是否能够成为一名优秀的猎人!?异想天开、壮烈精彩的冒险即将展开!!

playlists.title: Rokudo's Bad Girls [English Sub]
playlists.description:
All heroines in this story are "bad girls"!
The bullied boy is only popular with the "bad girls!"!
This is the love panic of the non-stop violent "bad girls"!

Tosuke Rokudo wished for a peaceful school life despite being bullied constantly at Amori Highschool that is full of delinquents. One day, a mysterious package from his supposedly dead grandfather came, then Rokudo received a strange power: the outrageous power of "unconditionally being super popular with 'bad girls' "!!

One after another, from female gangster to fashionistas and gang leaders, these bad girls with strong characters somehow showed their girly obedient and meek sides in front of Rokudo!

At first, Rokudo was perplexed, but as he got caught up in various fights and troubles caused by these bad girls, despite being timid, his hidden passionate and masculine sides started to bloom!

Although this was far from the ideal peaceful school life, being surrounded by the bad girls and his friends, his miserable days had started to take a turn, and here it begins, the odd school battle love panic!

playlists.title: 六道的恶女们 [中字]
playlists.description:
登场的女主角全都是 坏女人 ！
一个只受坏女人 百般喜爱 的 被欺负的男孩 ！！
势不可挡、由粗暴的坏女人们交织而成的 充满混乱的恋爱故事 ！

六道桃助虽然在充满不良少年的亚森高中备受欺负，但依然渴望着和平的校园生活。 
某天，六道收到了应该已经过世的祖父寄来的神秘卷轴，并获得了不可思议的力量。那就是“无条件受到‘坏女人’喜欢”不得了的惊人力量！！

那些接踵而来的女番长和辣妹等个性强烈的坏女人们，在六道面前不知为何都变成了老实乖巧、顺从听话的少女…！？

六道起初虽然感到困惑，但在不断被卷入以坏女人们为契机发生的各种战斗及麻烦的过程中，埋藏在个性懦弱的六道心中的热情与男子气概也开始渐渐萌发……。

虽然现在离理想中安稳的校园生活还很遥远，但在这群个性强烈的坏女人及朋友的围绕下，六道过去没出息的日子已经彻底转变，取而代之的充满校园战斗及混乱的恋爱故事，现在即将揭开序幕！！

playlists.title: Kuma Kuma Kuma Bear - Punch! [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Through an unexpected turn of events, Yuna, a shut-in gamer, is sent into another world by the hand of a self-proclaimed goddess.
Through the all-powerful bear gear she was gifted with, she has gained Super Bear Powers and Super Bear Magic. Not only that, thanks to her present-day knowledge, a dependable partner in Fina, and a strong bear mantle that could withstand all the whole other world shenanigans, she has completely grown used to this new world. In this world, Yuna plays with her friends, makes and eats delicious foods, lazes around, goes on an adventure every now and then, and lives free from day to day.
However, she does more than just relaxing and having fun.
When friends are in danger, monster attacks, bad guys scheming things, and many other kinds of troubles happen, Yuna will not leave things by.

playlists.title: I Got a CHEAT SKILL in ANOTHER WORLD and Became UNRIVALED in the REAL WORLD, Too [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Another World x Real World.
The boy who has leveled up becomes unrivaled in the two worlds...
A life-reversal fantasy begins!

Yuya Tenjo is a boy who has been severely bullied since childhood and despaired of his life.
One day, Yuya opens a "door to another world" that he found by chance.
As the first person to visit another world, he gains cheat-level abilities and achieves an astonishing level of improvement...
He was reborn as a perfect boy.
Furthermore, his level-up in another world begins to affect the real world as well.

playlists.title: 歌之王子殿下 真爱1000% (第1季) [中字]
playlists.description: 仰慕超人气偶像明星HAYATO，梦想成为作曲家的七海春歌，终于得偿宿愿，顺利进入竞争率高达200倍的艺能专门学校“早乙女学园”的作曲课程就读。在此，春歌将和偶像课程学生中的一人搭档组合，目标是在毕业时Shining事务所举办的新人选秀会中夺冠。然而春歌面前却出现了六位梦想成为偶像明星，光彩夺目的王子们。此外，再加上现任偶像明星的讲师阵容，以及不按牌理出牌的学园长的搅局，学园里总是处在事故的暴风圈中。到底春歌的搭档会是谁呢……！？比亲吻还要美妙的音乐响起，心跳加速的青春爱情喜剧。

playlists.title: Uta no Prince-sama 1000% [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Haruka Nanami, who dreams of becoming a composer and admires the popular idol HAYATO, gets her wish and enrolls in the composer course at the Saotome Academy, a performing arts school, where the competition for entry is 200 times higher than other schools. There, Haruka is paired with one of the students from the idol course and aims to pass the “Shining Office Newcomer Search Audition”, which is held at the time of graduation.
However, Haruka is confronted by six snow-white princes who dream of becoming idols. In addition, the school is always a storm of happenings, with its instructors who are active idols and its principal very unprecedented.
Who will be Haruka's pair now?
A heart-pounding adolescent love comedy story with music more beautiful than a kiss is about to unfold!

playlists.title: 再得一胜！ [中字]
playlists.description:
‘周刊少年Champion’人气连载中！
可爱又热血的柔道女孩日记电视动画化！

我要跟柔道一刀两断！
在高中里交个男朋友酸酸甜甜的度过三年。

晒伤时柔道服一摩擦就痛得要命，
因为寝技头发一掉就是一大把，
寒冬练习苦不堪言，
一下流鼻血一下骨折的，还会失去意识，
结果也没有变得多厉害，
我决定不练柔道了。

所以……所以拜托别让我想起来啦。
拿下一胜的痛快。

playlists.title: Ippon again! [English Sub]
playlists.description:
I'm so through with judo! I just want to live my bittersweet three years of high school with a boyfriend.

When I got sunburnt, my skin would rub against my judo uniform and hurt a lot, and when I tried doing a ground grappling technique, my hair would fall out all over the place. Not to mention the harsh mid-winter training, the nosebleeds, the broken bones, and fainting every time. I couldn't get stronger even with all that, so I decided to just quit.

So please... don't remind me of this again, will you? The good feeling of getting a score, an "ippon".

playlists.description:
被称为“怪异”的魑魅魍魉其实理所当然地存在在这个人世间。
担当“怪异”们的【智慧之神】的人类少女・岩永琴子，日复一日为了与“怪异”们有关的奇妙事件奔走。
而总是伴随在琴子身边的，是琴子一见钟情的对象、亦是连“怪异”们都视为怪物、避之唯恐不及的男人・樱川九郎。
本作为身世非凡的两人通力合作，以【虚构】面对“怪异”们所引起之各种脱离常理的神秘事件的故事。
两人联手挑战不可思议、 异想天开的事件究竟会有什么结果？两人的恋情又会有什么样的进展呢！？
〔恋爱×传奇×神秘〕再度来袭！！

playlists.title: (S2) BOFURI: I Don't Want to Get Hurt, so I'll Max Out My Defense. Season 2 [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Maple is obsessed with the VRMMO game "NewWorld Online".

She assigned all her points to defense, and at the beginning of the game, it seemed that she would have to spend a lot of time to get good. However, she has acquired several vicious skills; what unfolded was she trampling down the enemies again and again!

Her extraordinary gaming style led to her becoming a famous player who is treated as the "Last Boss".

The guild [Maple Tree], which she set up with her best friend Sally, also gathered a group of unique and reliable friends, and their unity was further strengthened.

And then…

A new floor has been updated in "NewWorld Online"!
She joins forces with former rivals, makes new friends, and even holds new events?!
Here, too, Maple and her friends are sure to go on the rampage…?

The world is expanding and the adventures are getting more and more fun!

playlists.title: 怕痛的我，把防御力点满就对了第二季 [中字]
playlists.description:
梅普露热衷于游玩VRMMO“NewWorld Online”。

她属性点全部点防御力，刚开始玩时还被人认为会变成皮很硬的磨队玩法，
结果她获得了好几个凶猛的技能，发展出的玩法则是一次又一次的蹂躏！
由于其不寻常的战斗英姿，她便成为了被当成“最终魔王”的知名玩家。

她与挚友莎莉一同创立的公会“大枫树”也聚集了充满个性且可靠的伙伴，
而他们之间的向心力也随着时间变得更加强大。

然后……

“NewWorld Online”的新阶层上线了！
梅普露等人将与曾经的劲敌携手合作、得到全新的伙伴，而游戏也将举办新活动！？
这种时候梅普露他们果然也一定会大闹特闹吗……？

世界逐渐拓展，冒险也将变得越来越有趣！

playlists.title: 银砂糖师与黑妖精～sugar apple fairy tale～ [中字]
playlists.description:
受到砂糖苹果指引的少女与妖精，两人的爱与梦谱出的动人童话故事

在一个人类奴役妖精，并相信砂糖果子会带来好运的世界──。在那里，制作神圣砂糖果子的特别砂糖果子职人被称为“银砂糖师”。
少女安的母亲生前是位顶尖的银砂糖师，她继承了母亲的志业，也立志成为一名银砂糖师。为此，她必须在一年一度的王都品评会上让众人认可她身为职人的实力。在前往王都的途中，安雇用了战士妖精夏尔作为她的护卫。虽然夏尔身为战士的本领了得，但由于他讲话刻薄又不相信人类，因此总是和安争吵不休。
然而，在与夏尔旅行的期间，安逐渐希望能和他成为朋友。跨越种族立场，克服困难情势，身为人类的安和身为妖精的夏尔共同谱出的未来会是──？

playlists.title: Sugar Apple Fairy Tale [English Sub]
playlists.description:
A girl and fairy guided by the sugar apples.
A glimmery fairy tale spun upon their dreams and love.

This is a world where humans use fairies and where candy is believed to bring about good fortune. There, a special candy crafter that crafts the venerated candy is called "Silver Sugar Master."

Anne, a girl whose late mother was a revered Silver Sugar Master, decides to inherit the craft and become Silver Sugar Master herself. To do that, she should prove her crafting skill at the royal capital's Royal Candy Fair. On the way to the royal capital city, she employed a warrior fairy named Challe as her bodyguard. Although Challe's ability as a warrior is true, he has a foul mouth and distrusts humans, thus, clashes with Anne are inevitable. However, as she continues her journey with Challe, Anne starts to desire friendship. Overcoming the differences in species and social standing as well as complicated circumstances, what kind of future will the human Anne and fairy Challe come to?

playlists.title: 转生公主与天才千金的魔法革命 [中字]
playlists.description:
帕雷提亚王国公主．艾妮丝菲亚．温．帕雷提亚拥有前世的记忆。
转生至魔法理所当然存在的世界，向往能够成为魔法师的艾妮丝菲亚，
她的梦想是用魔法翱翔于天际这件史无前例又缺乏常识的事。

然而艾妮丝菲亚不知为何无法使用魔法，
结果她尽管得到了怪咖公主的别称，仍日以继夜地做奇怪的研究。

某天晚上，艾妮丝菲亚用自制的魔女扫帚飞上天空。
而失控的扫帚飞进了贵族学院的晚宴中。

在那里，受众人誉为魔法天才的完美公爵千金尤菲莉亚，
正面临被艾妮丝菲亚的弟弟．亚尔加德王子当众宣言要取消婚约的窘境。
看到尤菲莉亚无声滑落的泪水，艾妮丝菲亚轻轻伸出手。

——这个魔法是为了你的笑容。
两位少女携手开拓未来，“转生╳天才”的魔法奇幻故事！

playlists.title: The Magical Revolution of the Reincarnated Princess and the Genius Young Lady [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Princess of the Kingdom of Pallettia, Anisphia "Anis" Wynn Pallettia, has memories of her previous life.
Reincarnated in a world where magic is commonplace, she dreams of becoming a wizard,
and aspires to be able to fly with magic, a crazy and insane thing to do.

But for some reason, Anisphia can't use magic.
She is nicknamed "Princess Odd" and spends her days and nights doing dubious research.

One night, Anisphia takes to the skies on her homemade witch broom. 
However, the uncontrollable broom jumps into a night party at the academy for nobles.

There, Euphyllia, the perfect duchess, rumored to be a magical genius,
is about to have her engagement annulled by Prince Algard, Anisphia's brother.
Seeing Euphyllia's tears shed silently, Anisphia gently reaches out to her.

向田刚志(穆寇达)是个平凡的上班族，某天突然被召唤到异世界。
他成了异世界的居民后，固有技能是“网路超市”。

playlists.title: 不相信人类的冒险者们好像要去拯救世界 [中字]
playlists.description:
隶属于帝涅兹圣王国的都市，特拉涅。
妄想一夕致富的冒险者们、机灵的商人、能歌善舞的吟游诗人、贵族、神官以及兽人族……。人们把这个职业和人种的大熔炉，本身就像个迷宫一样的城市称为“迷宫都市”。
被赶出冒险者队伍【武艺百般】，又被女友欺骗的落魄轻战士尼克也是这个城市的居民。
厌倦一切的他来到了一间酒馆。难吃的食物、四周欢乐的冒险者们、与他共桌的一群脸色惨淡的家伙……。
他像要把一切烦心事都抛到九霄云外似地猛灌酒。
“人类什么的能信个屁啊！！！！”
焦躁和不满不由自主地脱口而出。本该是只属于自己的这股情绪，却有四个人同时发出了相同声音──。
各自怀着创伤，属于他们的正宗冒险即将开幕！

playlists.title: Ningen Fushin: Adventurers Who Don't Believe in Humanity Will Save the World [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Terrane, a city belonging to the Holy Kingdom of Dinese. Many kinds of people gather in this city. Adventurers wanting to get rich, merchants with a keen eye, minstrels who sing and dance, aristocrats, priests, and beastmen... A melting pot of many professions and races, along with its maze-like structure earned the city the nickname of "Labyrinth City."
Nick, a light combatant that was kicked out of his party, the "Countless Art of Battle" and tricked by his girlfriend, is also a resident of this city.
Tired of it all, he went by a local bar. The bad foods, the cheerful adventurers around him, the silent people he's sharing a table with, the lukewarm beers... Fed up, he shouts, unknowingly followed by his tablemates.
"There's no way I can trust humans!!"
His frustration slipped through his mouth, but his tablemates shouted the same thing at the exact same time to his surprise.
These four people, each carrying their own wounds to lick, are about to start on a new adventure.

“UniteUp!”是由Sony Music献上的多次元偶像计划。

在突然开设的Youtube频道中，上传了形形色色的演出者丰富多元的歌曲。
从翻唱人气歌曲、公开“试唱”歌曲的“KIKUNOYU”、“EVAN”、“铃”，
以独立演出者身分发布具有高度音乐性之歌曲的“高尾大毅”、“二条锳士郎”、“东乡枫雅”。
以自己作曲的歌曲为中心展现独一无二之歌声的“春贺”。
藉由高水准的演出展现出压倒性之存在感的顶尖偶像“Anela”

由他们所共织出的歌曲及理念将会带来崭新的故事。

playlists.title: Reborn to Master the Blade: From Hero-King to Extraordinary Squire ♀ [English Sub]
playlists.description:
The Hero-King wished to be free and reincarnated as the strongest, beautiful, peerless knight!
Strongest gender change reincarnation fantasy!

Hero King Inglis became a "divine knight" with the blessing of a goddess, and established a vast kingdom. Eventually, just before he died in his old age, he strongly wished, "In a lifetime of serving my country and my people, I couldn't master my skills. In my next life, I want to live for myself and train to my limits."
His wish was heard by the goddess, and he's reincarnated into the far future.

However, that Hero King's born as the "daughter" of a famous knight family!? And for some reason, she is labeled as an unqualified knight.

"If anything, it's convenient for me. I can stay on the front line without getting promoted. There's no better training than actual combat!"

She aims to enroll in the Knights' Academy to train as a squire for her childhood friend, Rafinha.
The legend of the world's strongest beautiful squire begins!

playlists.title: Woodpecker Detective’s Office [English Sub]
playlists.description:
It is the end of the Meiji Era.
The genius poet Ishikawa Takuboku, who’s struggling financially, starts a detective business out of his lodging in response to a certain murder case.
He calls it the Woodpecker Detective’s Office. "The ghosts of the Twelve-Story Tower in Asakusa," "the man-eating figure who wanders the streets on snowy nights"...
Takuboku involves himself in one bizarre case after another with his hometown acquaintance, Kindaichi Kyosuke, as his assistant.

playlists.title: My Senpai is Annoying [English Sub]
playlists.description:
It is Igarashi Futaba's second year at Itomaki Corporation, and she really wants to be a respected employee as soon as possible!
She is watched over by her senpai, Takeda Harumi, who although is quite the crass guy, is also very caring towards her.
Even though Futaba finds Takeda-senpai annoying, actually there are times where he's not that bad… But he really is annoying!
Based on the hotly popular web-comic that broke the record for the highest number of likes on Twitter in 2017 (1 chapter = 415,000 likes), and won first place in the Web Manga category in the Up-and-coming Manga Awards 2018 - My Senpai is Annoying!
The long-awaited anime adaptation of this everyday romantic comedy about struggling working adults is coming soon!

playlists.title: Girls' Last Tour [English Sub]
playlists.description: "Get along with despair." The civilization where humans prosper and thrive has collapsed for a long time. Every living being live constantly with death, it's a world where everything is already over. All that remains is a giant city that has turned into ruin and machines that have rotted away with time. When did the world end, and why did the world end? In the last moments of the world, where those things aren't even questioned anymore, two girls are on their own, Chito, and Yuuri. Riding on their favorite Kettenkrad, they roam around the endless ruins, without any destination. In a world where everything is heading towards its end, the apocalypse fantasy tour story of the girls will start now.

playlists.title: Accel World [English Sub]
playlists.description: Set in the year 2046, Neuro-Synchronization allows humans to virtually manipulate their five senses, where people can access the internet and enter virtual worlds via Neuro-Linkers. The series follows Haruyuki "Haru" Arita, a short, fat boy who has low self-esteem due to being bullied at school which Haru vents his frustrations in virtual world games. Haruyuki soon gets the attention of Kuroyukihime, the Student Council Vice-President who invites him into the "Accelerated World" called Brain Burst, a program that allows users to make time appear to stand still in their surroundings by "accelerating" their brainwaves in the real world. But in order to gain more points to accelerate, Brain Burst users fight each other in a virtual reality massive multiplayer online (VRMMO) fighting game where losing all of your points means you can never use Brain Burst again. Grateful for helping him, Haruyuki vows to help Kuroyukihime defeat the "Six Kings of Color", the leaders of the most powerful factions in Brain Burst and obtain Level 10 to ultimately learn why the "Accelerated World" was created.

playlists.title: 圣剑传说 Legend of Mana -The Teardrop Crystal- [中字]
playlists.description: 夏罗是个住在多米纳小镇附近的少年。某个时候起，他开始会在梦中听到神秘的声音，告诉他自己有使命在身……。某天，夏罗遇见了两个“珠魅”。珠魅是在过去，由于镶在其胸前的宝石遭觊觎，而有许多人被杀害的种族。而现在，神秘的宝石小偷在世界各地接二连三掀起袭击珠魅的事件。夏罗即将踏上一场围绕着珠魅宝石的冒险旅程！

playlists.title: Legend of Mana -The Teardrop Crystal- [English Sub]
playlists.description:
There was once a young boy named Shiloh who lives near the city of Domina. From who knows when, he starts to hear a mysterious voice inside his dream, telling him that he has a duty to fulfill.

One day, he meets a pair of "Jumi."

Jumi is a tribe of humanoid gem people that was driven to near-extinction due to people hunting the jewels embedded in their chests.

With the appearance of a mysterious "Jewel Hunter", more and more Jumi people are attacked all over the world.

Thus Shiloh embarks on a journey about the Jumi and their jewels!

playlists.title: 路人超能100 (S3) [中字]
playlists.description:
当某种数值来到“100”时，就会爆发的少年──路人。
他的外表极为普通，却是个强悍的超能力者。
他在神棍师父──灵幻新隆经营的灵能谘询所帮忙处理麻烦的委托，在这样的日子中，他希望的安稳日子会到来吗？然而超能力却会以青春为原动力失控！
世界引领期盼的系列动画第三季！

playlists.title: 被勇者队伍开除的驭兽使、邂逅了最强种的猫耳少女 [中字]
playlists.description:
“雷因，你被开除了”

驭兽使雷因与勇者一同以打倒魔王为目标。
但在某天遭同伴斥责为废物，遭勇者队伍开除。

雷因选择了自由生活的冒险者之道，他在测验的途中遇到了被魔物袭击的少女奏。
为了让奏逃脱雷因挺身而出，但她却一击就打倒了魔物。

没想到奏居然是有着非比寻常力量的“最强种”之一，猫灵族的少女。
被雷因的才能和温柔吸引的奏向他这么说

“要试着使役我看看吗？”

雷因和最强的猫耳少女订下契约，迈向身为冒险者的崭新人生。
但开除雷因的勇者们，以及其他的“最强种”也发现了他的力量。

playlists.title: Beast Tamer [English Sub] | From 2nd October, 22:00 (GMT+8)
playlists.description:
"Rein. You're fired."

Rein is a beast tamer who aims to defeat the demon king along with the hero.
But one day, he was called useless by his friends and was banished from the hero's party.

Rein who decided to live freely as an adventurer, encountered Kanade, a girl who was attacked by a demon beast when he was taking his exam.。

It turns out, Kanade is a girl from one of the strongest tribes that hold abnormal power, the cat tribe!
Kanade who was drawn by Rein's talents and kindness told this to Rein.

"Would you like to try and control me?"

Rein made a contract with the strongest cat-eared girl and starts his new life as a beginner adventurer.
But, the hero's party who banished Rein, and another strongest tribe noticed his power...

playlists.title: 入间同学入魔了 第3季 [中字]
playlists.description:
“入间同学入魔了！”是一部描写人类少年・铃木入间成为魔界的大恶魔萨利班的孙子，
并进入他担任理事长、恶魔们就读的恶魔学校中念书的奋斗及成长的故事。

在第三季，入间即将面对的下一道试练是——
勇闯魔界的巨大丛林、收集食物的竞赛《收获祭》！
班上同学们将成为彼此的竞争对手，
充满魄力的肉搏战&考验智谋的战斗即将开始！？

playlists.title: Welcome To Demon School! Iruma-kun Season 3 [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Welcome to the fun-filled Netherworld!! 

Due to an unexpected sequence of events, Suzuki Iruma, a good-natured boy who can't say no to others, became the grandson of Sullivan, the great Demon of the Netherworld! And so, as he is doted on by the demon Sullivan, Iruma began to attend the demon school where Sullivan is the chair-demon... 

Hiding his identity as a human, Iruma only wishes to live a peaceful school life, but for one reason or another he always ended up being the center of attention. Getting into fights with elite demons, befriending an oddball(?) female demon, and furthermore, even being kept an eye on by the strict student council president! 

But with his natural kindness, Iruma overcomes these troubles one after another!

playlists.title: 妖怪旅馆营业中 [中字]
playlists.description: 女大学生津场木葵继承了过世祖父看得见妖怪的力量，某天，突然被抓到座落于妖怪鬼神们所居住的隐世之中的百年老铺旅馆“天神屋”。困惑的葵被告知其祖父欠下了巨债，以及当时约定好将她嫁入鬼神的大老板家当作借款的担保品一事。葵不愿从命，为了拒绝这桩婚事，向妖怪们宣言要在天神屋工作来还债，但……。

playlists.title: Kakuriyo -Bed & Breakfast for Spirits- [English Sub]
playlists.description: Aoi Tsubaki is suddenly swept away to the hidden realm when a handsome ogre lord comes to take her as his wife! He claims that she must pay back her grandfather’s debt, but Aoi’s not willing to give her hand over so easily. Instead, she makes a deal to work at the Tenjin-ya, a bed and breakfast for ayakashi, to pay back what her family owes.as she wins the spirits over one dish at a time, Aoi will find much more than a job in this hidden realm.

playlists.title: 黄金神威 [中字]
playlists.description: 明治时代后期。有着“不死之身杉元”外号的日俄战争英雄．杉元佐一，他为了某个目的需要一大笔钱，因而来到了北海道。在那里，他无意间听说有一笔从爱奴人手中夺来的巨额财宝的传闻。这是能够一夕致富的大好机会。据说宝藏被收监于网走监狱的男人藏了起来，而刻在24名越狱犯身上的刺青正是说明宝藏所在地的线索。过程之中，杉元遭受到棕熊的袭击，并且被一名爱奴人少女所救。这位名叫阿席莉帕的少女，她的父亲过去遭抢夺宝藏的男人所杀。紧接着，有如呼应杉元的行动一般，从以前就一直以宝藏为目标在暗中行动的北方最强部队．第七师团，以及背负刺青的越狱犯们的行动也开始浮上台面。这场以雄伟的北方大地为故事舞台，为求一夕致富的生存竞赛究竟会如何发展？

playlists.title: Golden Kamuy [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Late Meiji era. The Russo-Japanese war hero, Sugimoto Saichi, nicknamed "the Immortal Sugimoto", is in Hokkaido to acquire a large sum of money for a specific purpose. There, he is offered the chance to get rich from the huge reserves of gold stolen from the Ainu people. The reserves are hidden by a man imprisoned in Abashiri Prison, and the tattoos on the bodies of 24 escaped prisoners are said to be clues to its whereabouts.
Then, Sugimoto is attacked by a brown bear, and an Ainu girl saves him. The girl, whose name is Asirpa, had her father killed by the man who took the buried gold. As if in response to Sugimoto's actions, the 7th Division, the most powerful unit in the north, and escaped prisoners with tattoos on their backs, who have long been in the dark for the buried gold, also start to make their movements known. What will become of the get-rich-quick survival that has been taking place in the magnificent northern lands?

playlists.description:
In the parallel of Ente Isla, they were the Overlord and the Hero. But in modern-day Tokyo, they are hardworking employees of the modern world under new identities, Sadao Maou and Emi Yusa. 

Along with his two confidants at the Overlord's Castle, and a loving high school girl, Chiho, Maou is getting used to life in Japan, while also struggling with the rough economic times. One day, a mysterious little girl appears and the Overlord's Castle is in turmoil! 

The Overlord’s Castle is tasked with raising a child, while visitors from Ente Isla keep coming in. They also have to work to support the people living in the Overlord's Castle, which is a miserable six-mat room! And so the part-timer Overlord's folksy fantasy unfolds once again in the second season of the anime!

playlists.title: FUUTO PI [English Sub] | From 1st August 2022, every Monday at 00:00 (GMT+8)
playlists.description:
The wind never stopped blowing in that city.
 It carries everything. Even small joy, even grand misfortune.
 
 Such is the city of the wind, Fuuto.
 
 "Museum", the organisation that once threatened the city, has been brought to its destruction by the Kamen Riders. However, the very dangerous item that they have massively produced, the "Gaia Memories", are still scattered all over the place, secretly distributed within the emotionally turbulent Fuuto. There is no end to the people transformed by the memory into the monstrous"Dopant".
 
 Shotaro Hidari, a "half-boiled" private investigator held back by his kindness, and Philip, the genius private investigator and Shotaro's forever partner. Today in Narumi Detective Agency where the two work, comes a bizarre request.
 
 As the wind stops blowing, mysterious shadows have started moving within the city. As Shotaro meets the mysterious devilish beauty, Tokime, his fate starts to change.
 And thus a new case envelops Shotaro & Philip, the two in one detective, also known as Kamen Rider W.
 
 It has been 13 years since the TV show aired in 2009.
 The story of Kamen Rider W has moved from live-action to manga, and now to another new stage. The true sequel of the story, "Fuuto PI", finally moves into anime!

playlists.title: 风都侦探 [中字]
playlists.description: 风不断地吹拂着这座城市。无论是小小的幸福，还是重大的不幸，都是乘风而来。风的城市──风都。过去威胁这座城市的组织“博物馆”，已由假面骑士们逼入绝境。可是，该组织所大量生产的危险道具“盖亚记忆体”仍四散在各处。记忆体在各种情绪呼啸着的风都之中暗地里散播，藉由记忆体的力量变成怪人“掺杂体”的人们依旧络绎不绝。因为温柔而显得优柔寡断的“半吊子硬汉”侦探──左翔太郎。头脑派侦探，也是他永远的伙伴──菲力普。两人身处的鸣海侦探事务所，今天也有人带来奇异的委托。在风声静止的城市中暗中活动的神秘黑影。以及突然出现的魔性美女──时女。与她的相遇改变了翔太郎的命运。翔太郎&菲力普，两人一体的侦探──假面骑士W的新事件即将开幕──2009年电视播放后历经13年。舞台从真人转向漫画，至今仍然不断发展周边故事的“假面骑士W”。该作品的正统续篇“风都侦探”，终于成为动画跃动起来!!

playlists.description: Kanji Yakutani is a pharmaceutical researcher in modern Japan. He woke up one day and found that he had been reborn as Falma de Médicis, a son of a court pharmacist from the respected de Médicis family. Falma was shocked upon seeing the world's medicinal field being dominated by false procedure and drug formulations as well as popular practices like magic and spell that could not be regarded as medical practice at all. Making use of the modern pharmaceutical knowledge that he has, along with the overpowering ability of "Substance Creation & Substance Elimination" which he gained in the parallel world as part of "Divine Arts" only the noble family can use, he faced various illnesses upon him. And so, he produced effective drugs known as "Parallel World Pharmacy" and spread them to the people. Parallel World power x modern pharmacy!  The fantasy that changes the future of the medical field in an alternate world and saves people, begins now!

playlists.description:
某一天，极其普通的平凡大学生雨宫夕日眼前出现了一只会说话的蜥蜴，并被它请托协助解决“地球的危机”。
还来不及拒绝就成为“兽之骑士团”一员的夕日在因为戒指的力量而获得了名为“掌握领域”的超能力后不久就遭遇到敌人的袭击。
在夕日陷入走投无路的危机时出手拯救他的，竟然是住在夕日家隔壁的少女・五月雨。
原以为救世主终于降临，但没想到五月雨其实是企图征服地球的魔王……。
受到她不可理喻的强大力量以及魔王魅力所吸引的夕日成为了她的下仆，并为她所期望实现的另一个目的提供协助。

playlists.title: Classroom of the Elite Season 2 [English Sub] | From 4th July 2022, every Monday at 21:00 (GMT+8)
playlists.description:
Tokyo Metropolitan Advanced Nurturing High School.
The school boasts a 100% advancement rate and employment rate, and students receive points equivalent to 100,000 yen in cash every month.
It is a paradise-like school, but in reality, it is a school that judges its students based on merit, where only a few students with excellent grades receive favorable treatment.
Kiyotaka Ayanokoji is assigned to Class D, a class full of problem children, and he cooperates with his classmate Suzune Horikita, who is aiming for promotion to Class A.
After completing a survival test on a deserted island, the students enjoys a brief rest on a luxury cruise ship, but then a new special exam is about to begin, in which each class is involved. Will it be for the class, for the group, or for the individual?
While the other classes are showing disturbing behaviour, Class D, which lacks cohesion, finds itself in a tight spot.
Can the students, torn between trust and suspicion, see through the truth?
A new school apocalypse is about to unveil once again.

playlists.description:
东京都高度育成高等中学。
标榜升学率、就职率达百分之百，每个月会提供相当于十万圆的点数，是一间乐园学校。但其实是一间只有成绩优秀的人，才拥有优良待遇的实力至上主义学校。
绫小路清隆被分配到问题学生云集的D班，决定帮助同班同学堀北铃音升上A班。

当别班的人展开可疑的行动，欠缺团结的D班陷入困境当中。
在信赖与猜疑的夹缝中行动的学生们，能看破真相吗？
全新的校园启示录，现在再度开幕。

playlists.title: Made in Abyss: The Golden City of the Scorching Sun [English Sub] | From 6th July 2022 at 22:30 (GMT+8)
playlists.description:
Every place in the world has been explored to every nook and cranny, with the sole exception being the great giant hole known as the Abyss. Nobody knows how deep the pit runs, and it is filled many weird creatures and valuable relics that cannot be recreated with current technology. The many mysteries of the Abyss draws upon many to start an adventure. After generations, those adventurers that have challenged the depth of the Abyss are now known as the Cave Raiders. Riko, the child that lives in an orphanagee at the city of Orth, has intertwined fate with the Abyss. She dreams of one day becoming a legendary cave raider like her mother and unveil the mystery of the Abyss. One day, the white whistle of her mother, Lyza, was discovered along with a message, driving Riko to explore the depth of the Abyss. Reg, a robot that lost his memories and was then found by Riko is also determined to accompany in her journey.
 
 At the 4th layer, Riko suffered from the venoms of an Orb Piercer, but she was rescued by Nanachi, a hollow. After Nanachi joined the group, they advanced into the 5th layer where Bondrewd, a White Whistle, awaits. There, they met Prushka, a girl raised by Bondrewd that doesn't know about life outside the Abyss. Prushka becomes engrossed after listening to Riko's tale of adventure and wishes to go with her, but unfortunately she was used by Bondrewd in an experiment. However, Prushka then becomes Riko's white whistle, and they all went into the 6th layer, The Capital of the Unreturned, where a village of Hollows living with their own unique sense of values lies.

playlists.title: 来自深渊 烈日的黄金乡 [中字]
playlists.description:
在已被彻底探索殆尽的世界里，名为“深渊”的大洞是硕果仅存的秘境。

这个深不见底、不知会延伸到何处的巨大垂直洞穴中，不仅栖息着各种稀奇古怪的生物，还沉睡着现今人类所做不出来的珍贵遗物。

“深渊”那处处充满不可思议的神秘样貌，吸引人们前仆后继地前去冒险。渐渐地，大家开始将那些多次挑战大洞的冒险者们称为“探窟家”。

孤儿莉可住在兴建于深渊四周的城镇“奥斯”，她梦想着将来要成为像她母亲一样伟大的探窟家，并一解深渊之谜。

某天，她母亲莱萨的白笛被人发现，让莉可因此下定决心要潜入深渊的深处。她捡到的失忆机器人雷格，也为了寻找自己的记忆而决定与她同行。

莉可在深界四层被穿珠的毒给侵蚀折磨，拯救她的是名叫奈奈祈的惨剧终末。
奈奈祈加入之后，三个人便继续前往彭多尔多所在的深界五层冒险。在那里，他们遇见了一个自称普鲁修卡的女孩。由彭多尔多抚养长大的她对外界一无所知。
普鲁修卡深深着迷于莉可的冒险故事，并希望能和莉可一起冒险，然而她却惨遭彭多尔多利用来做实验。

不过后来普鲁修卡改变形体，变成莉可的白笛，与她一同朝深界六层“不归之都”前进。
在那里有座“惨剧终末的村子”，那是拥有自己一套价值观的惨剧终末们所生活的地方。

playlists.description: In a world that has seen its every corner explored, the huge chasm called the "Abyss" stands as the last unknown frontier. Within this deep pit, the ultimate depth of which is still unknown, strange creatures live among valuable sleeping relics that today's human technology is unable to reproduce. The mysterious formation that is the Abyss mesmerizes people and urges them to venture inside. These adventurers, who continue to challenge the Abyss time and time again, have come to be known as "cave raiders." In the city of Orth, which has taken rise at the edge of the Abyss, lives an orphan named Riko. She dreams of someday becoming a legendary cave raider like her mother and of unraveling the mysteries of the Abyss. One day while Riko is cave raiding in the Abyss, she comes across a robot who looks like a human boy...

playlists.title: A Certain Scientific Railgun S [English Sub]
playlists.description: With a total population of 2.3 million, the huge city occupies most of the western part of Tokyo. About 80% of its population are students, so the city is known as the 'Academy City', where the development of supernatural powers, which twist the laws of the world to create supernatural phenomena, takes place.Students who have undergone special classes (curriculum) and gained abilities are evaluated in six levels from 'no ability (level 0)' to 'super ability (level 5)' through periodic physical examinations (system scan). Standing at the top of the list, and being described as the strongest, are the seven 'Level 5 psychics'.One of them is Mikoto Misaka. She is a top-level "Electromaster" who can manipulate electricity at will, and is also known as "Railgun", a 14-year-old girl who attends the prestigious Tokiwadai Middle School for young ladies. Kuroko Shirai is a junior student and a member of the Judgment. Her colleague Shikari Hatsuharu, who yearns to be a lady, and her friend Ruiko Saten, who loves urban legends. With these friends, Mikoto is leading a peaceful, ordinary and slightly unusual everyday life in the academy city, when suddenly the "darkness" of the academy city closes in on her...

playlists.title: A Certain Magical Index [English Sub]
playlists.description:
The stage is set in A huge city occupying most of western Tokyo, Academy City, is called so because about 80% of the total population of 2,300,000 people are students, and the students who live there have a special curriculum to develop their psychic abilities, and are assessed on a six-levels scale depending on their abilities, ranging from Level 0 to Level 5.
Our main character, Toma Kamijo, is a high school student in Academy City, but is rated at Level 0, putting him on the verge of flunking out of school. In his right hand there is an ability called "Imagine Breaker" which cancels out "any other power."
On the first day of summer vacation, a sister in a pure white nun's habit suddenly fall from the sky in his room. She calls herself "Index" who has escaped from the world of magic, and sorcerers have rushed in pursuit of her. They want the 103,000 grimoires inside Index's head. In the battle Kamijo is forced to get involved in, and destroys the magic that has been cast on Index with his right hand, and in exchange for freeing her from her sad fate, he loses his memory.
Toma spends his days trying not to let anyone know that he has lost his memory, but one incident after another befalls him.
When science and magic cross paths, the story begins.

playlists.description: 每一个人，都有不能展现给任何人看的一面──这是个世界各国都在台面下进行激烈情报战的时代。东国与西国，两国之间已持续冷战了十多年。隶属于西国情报局对东课〈WISE〉的干练间谍〈黄昏〉，被指派一项极机密任务，奉命接近威胁东西和平的危险人物，要刺探出东国国家统一党党魁──唐纳文．戴斯蒙德的战争计划。其任务名为──行动代号〈枭〉。任务内容是：“在一周内组好家庭，并潜入戴斯蒙德儿子所就读的名校。”于是〈黄昏〉扮起精神科医生──洛伊德．佛杰，开始组织家庭。然而，他找到的女儿．安妮亚是会读心的超能力者，妻子．约儿则是位暗杀者！由于利害一致，三人便互相隐瞒真实身分，并展开共同生活。世界的和平，就这样被托付给状况百出的临时家庭──

playlists.title: The Dawn of the Witch [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Saybil is a student of the academy of magic, however, he has no memories of his life before entering the academy. 
His daily life at the academy is full of emptiness as he himself couldn't figure out why he was here in the first place. 
Without any motivation, his grade is always among the lowest. 
One day, the principal, Albus, suddenly sent Saybil to a dangerous special training.
"I want you to spread words of the usefulness of magic in a land where witch hunts exist."
It has been years after the end of the war between the witches and the church, 
but society hasn't fully accepted both witches and magic.
It is the dawn of the witch.
This is a self-discovery story of an ordinary boy and his friends with a hidden past.

我想不起来。
想不起自己究竟是什么人──。

魔法学校的学生赛维尔没有入学前的记忆。
不知道自己为何在此的他总感觉学校生活有些空虚，不懂得该如何努力的他成绩总是垫底。

playlists.description: 名留于神话，史上最强的“魔王”瓦尔瓦德斯。他将人生鞠躬尽瘁于王的身分，由太过强大而变得孤单，因而向往起平凡的生活，为此转生到数千年后的世界，成了村民亚德．梅堤欧尔。不过，转生来到的未来，魔法文明衰退，魔法本身已经劣化。亚德和第一个朋友也是青梅竹马的伊莉娜一起进入魔法学园就读，即使他再怎么否认自己的特别，也藏不起破格的实力。对他怀抱敬畏之心的人、向他求爱的人都络绎不绝，又有过去曾让世界陷于恐怖之中的“魔族”开始暗地里行动……昔日的“魔王”可以得到安稳平凡的人生吗？波澜不断的学园英雄奇幻故事，就此开幕！

playlists.title: The Greatest Demon Lord Is Reborn as a Typical Nobody -  [ENG Sub]
playlists.description:
Valvatos, whose name was engraved in mythology, was the strongest Demon King in history.

Weary of his life as a King, he yearns for an ordinary life - an escape from the loneliness caused by his strength.
Thus, he reincarnated into a young man named Ard Meteor, born as a typical villager a thousand years later.

However, in this reincarnated future, magical civilization is in decline.
Magic itself was weakening.

It was in this era that Ard entered a Magic Academy with his first friend since childhood, Irina.
However, no matter how much he tried to reject being special, he couldn't hide his extraordinary powers.

Because of this, there was a ceaseless throng of people who were in awe of him, and who wants to get closer to him.
Moreover, the 'demons' who once terrorized the world had also begun to stir.

Can the former Demon King live a peaceful and mediocre life that he longed for?
A turbulent Heroic School-Fantasy has begun!

playlists.title: His and Her Circumstances [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Like a drug, Yukino Miyazawa was addicted to admiration and praise from those around her. She worked hard to become the perfect student, the perfect girl. But that was before... him. Souichirou Arima.

The instant she met him, she hated him. Without even trying, he snatched the very glory from her hands by easily acing the high school entrance exam that should have made her the class representative. To take back what is rightfully hers, Yukino is putting all her efforts into plotting her revenge - but was love part of the plan?

playlists.title: 小书痴的下克上:为了成为图书管理员不择手段! S3 [中字]
playlists.description: 打造一个所有人都能读到书的世界，成为神殿的青衣见习巫女的梅茵，和路兹、多莉以及孤儿院的孩子们一起制作了儿童用的圣典绘本。对书本的热情有增无减的梅茵，赋予了约翰与海蒂"古腾堡"的封号后，向下一个目标"活版印刷"迈进。然而，梅茵的前方却是一片乌云笼罩。察觉到拥有强大魔力与奇异知识的梅茵具有利用价值的贵族、以及对梅茵怀恨在心的贵族，暗中盯上了梅茵。为了人身安全，梅茵身边配属了护卫骑士。斐迪南更下令要梅茵成为身属贵族的卡斯泰德之养女。虽然这道命令是为了保护梅茵的安全，但不想与重要家人分开的梅茵并无法接受。此时，梅茵家诞生了新的生命。伊娃生下了加米尔，梅茵成为了姐姐。此外，神殿决定抚养被遗弃的身蚀之子．戴尔克，见习侍从戴莉雅则把戴尔克视为自己的家人一般疼爱。随着想守护的事物越来越多，袭击梅茵的魔爪也越来越逼近。梅茵的境遇将会变得如何呢！？

playlists.title: Ascendance of a Bookworm S3 [English Sub]
playlists.description:
To a world where anyone can read books!

Myne who became an apprentice to the blue shrine maiden of the temple, worked with Lutz, Tuuli, and the children of the orphanage to create a scripture picture book for children.
Myne's passion for books is only growing. Give Johan and Heidi the title of Gutenberg and aim for the next goal, letterpress printing.

However, a dark cloud rushes into Myne's path.
The aristocrats who found great value in Myne, who has great magical power and mysterious knowledge, and the aristocrats who have grudge against Myne, are secretly targeting her.

For her safety, Myne starts to have an escort knight.
In addition, Ferdinand orders Myne to be the adopted daughter of the aristocrat Karstedt.
That order was made to protect Myne, but she cannot accept Mine who does not want to leave her dear family.

Meanwhile, a new life is born in Myne's family.
Effa gives birth to Kamil, and Myne became an older sister.
And then, the temple decided to raise Dirk, an abandoned child who eats a lot. Delia, an apprentice attendant, loves Dirk so much as if he's a part of her own family.

As the number of things Myne want to protect increased, the evil hands aiming at Myne kept on approaching.
What will happen to Myne!?

playlists.title: The Familiar of Zero [English Sub]
playlists.description: In a world where magic is a reality, the young Louise is at the bottom of her class. Dubbed "Zero" by her classmates at Tristein Academy (due to her zero success rate for magic), Louise (along with all first year students) was charged with summoning a familiar; and instead of a cute magical creature, the familiar arrived in the form of... Saito Hiraga, a normal Japanese boy who was abruptly teleported from his own world?! Can both Louise and Saito come to terms with their new and complicated "relationship" and (more importantly) help Saito find a way home?

playlists.title: BLACK BULLET [English Sub]
playlists.description: Gastrea, grotesque-looking parasitic lifeforms suddenly appeared. With their red-sparkling eyes, overwhelming strength, and abnormal regeneration capabilities, humanity doesn't stand a chance against their invasion. Now that humanity had lost half of its territory, they live in a place surrounded by monoliths made from the only metal Gastrea are weak against, "Varanium." They have no other choice than to live in fear of Gastrea, hiding inside the small Area. In such a situation, the humanity that survived formed an organization, and it consists of specialists that have a way to fight Gastrea. They're called "Civil Security Agency," shortened as "Civil Officer." Amongst them, is Rentaro Satomi, a high school boy that's affiliated with Tendo Civil Security Agent. Along with his partner, Aihara Enju, he got involved in schemes that might bring destruction into Tokyo.

playlists.title: The King of Braves GaoGaiGar [English Sub]
playlists.description: In the year 2005, a race of alien monsters called Zondars emerge from underground and launch a series of attacks on the city of Tokyo. The only defense against these creatures is the secret agency known as the Gutsy Geoid Guard (or 3G) and their ultimate weapon, the awesome giant robot GaoGaiGar. GaoGaiGar's pilot, Guy Shishio, is a former astronaut who was nearly killed two years before when the Zondars first crashed to earth. Guy's life was spared when a mysterious robot lion called Galeon pulled him from the burning shuttle and brought him to Earth. Guy's father, Leo, then used Galeon's technology to rebuild his shattered son as a cyborg, in the hopes that he could stop the aliens when they appear. Now, with Galeon as its core, GaoGaiGar fights to protect Earth. He is aided by a team of transforming robots and by a young boy named Mamoru, who has the power to purify the Zondars' cores, and seems to be connected to the mysterious Galeon.

playlists.title: Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World- Season 2 [English Sub]
playlists.description:
▶️ 《Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World-》 
🔥 Full Series Playlist： 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLwLSw1_eDZl3RN7t6wesJqlUkSUN6FHKF
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
A reunion that was supposed to spell the arrival of peaceful times is quickly shattered when Subaru Natsuki and Emilia return to Irlam village. Witnessing the devastation left behind by the calamities known as Sin Archbishops, Subaru sinks into the depths of despair as his ability to redo proves futile.
As the group makes their way to the Sanctuary in search of answers, Subaru has an unexpected encounter with the Witch of Greed—Echidna. Subjected to her untamed rhythm, he is forced to dive into the spirals of the past and future. At the same time, several mysterious threats set their sights on the Sanctuary, heralding a horrific fate for the hapless people trapped within.
Everlasting contracts, past sins, and unrequited love will clash and submerge into a river of blood in the second season of Re:Zero kara Hajimeru Isekai Seikatsu. Pushed to the brink of hopelessness, how long will Subaru's resolve to save his loved ones last?

playlists.title: Hakata Tonkotsu Ramens [English Sub]
playlists.description:
"There is a person you desperately want to kill. Now, how do you kill that person?" 
At a glance, Fukuoka seems like a peaceful town, but crime runs rampant behind the scenes. 
It's now a battleground for professional killers, with urban legends suggesting that there's even one who specializes in killing professional killers.
Assassins, detectives, revenge seekers, informants, torture specialists... 
When stories are told of these and other professionals of the underground, a "killer of professional killers" appears...

playlists.title: 博多豚骨拉面团 [中字]
playlists.description: “假设你现在有个无论如何都想杀掉的人，请问你会怎么杀死他？”福冈，乍看之下似乎是个和平的城市，但其实暗地里犯罪行为四处蔓延。如今已经成为了杀手们的激战区，甚至有了”专杀杀手的杀手”这种都市传说。杀手、侦探、复仇专家、情报商人、拷问师etc－－当围绕着地下社会的男人们的故事交织汇聚，‘刺客杀手’悄然现身－－。第20回电击小说大奖＜大奖＞得奖作品！

playlists.title: High School Prodigies Have It Easy Even in Another World! [English Sub]
playlists.description:
An aeroplane accident befalls seven high school students.
When they regain consciousness, it's in a world of magic and half-animal humans.
Thrown into a feudalistic society run by autocrats and guilds
with not a modern convenience in sight, these high schoolers don't even sweat it!

No electricity?
They build a nuclear power plant.

Need to make a little money?
They take over economic control of the city.

How to repay their gratitude to an oppressed citizenry?
They upend the corrupt nobility by going to war.

Not just any high schoolers, these teenagers are super prodigies, standing atop their fields of politics, economics, science, medicine, journalism, martial arts and prestidigitation! They are the world's Dream Team of intellectual, technological and physical prowess, starring in a delightful tale of virtue over vice in an otherworldly revolution!

playlists.title: 超人高中生们即便在异世界也能从容生存！ [中字]
playlists.description:
七名高中生被卷入了飞机的意外事故之中。
当他们醒来时，却发现自己身处于存在着魔法与兽人的异世界之中。
事情发生得太过突然，使得他们陷入了混乱…然而并没有（！？）。
他们先是在没有电力的世界打造了发电厂、出去赚点小钱然后就支配了大都市的经济，后来甚至为了向受恶政所苦的恩人们报恩，与无良的贵族们打起了战争，在异世界简直为所欲为！？

没错，这七人都不是普通的高中生，
他们全都是在政治、经济、科学与医疗领域君临顶点的超人高中生！

这是拥有地球最优秀之睿智与技术的梦幻团队，
毫无保留地运用超高级科技展开的异世界革命物语！

playlists.title: The Genius Prince's Guide to Raising a Nation Out of Debt [English Sub]
playlists.description: Natra Kingdom, a kingdom that's being exposed to the threat of a hegemony kingdom. Wein, a prince who had to handle the burden of the country even though he's still young, used his brilliance, and starts to show great achievements with the support of his aide, Ninym. "But this country...Is a dead end!" He wants to meddle with internal affairs, but there's no money. There's not enough army to take money from somewhere else. People who are brilliant and decent, are moving to other countries. "I just want to sell this country quick, and flee" Wein's dream is to retire quickly, and live a quiet and comfortable life. If he flatters a big kingdom, and sell the kingdom to them, he should be able to achieve his dream. But, the diplomacy and military develops in a way that's outside of his predictions? Shake the world with wisdom and quick thinking. The small and weak kingdom management by a genius prince, open its curtain here!

playlists.title: 天才王子的赤字国家重生术 [中字]
playlists.description:
暴露在霸权国家威胁下的弱小国家．纳特拉王国。
年纪轻轻就得背负这个国家的王子维恩，在辅佐官妮妮姆的协助下，活用自己的才能，以他灵活的手腕治理着这个国家。

可是这个国家……在各方面都很惨！

就算想重整内政也没钱。
也没有军力去侵略他国夺取资源。
像样的优秀人才都流失到其他国家去了。

“我好想赶快卖掉这个国家逃之夭夭啊！”

维恩的愿望就是能早点去隐居，过着悠然自得的生活。
只要讨好大国，卖掉这个国家就能实现他的梦想了。
可是外交和军事都朝着他意想不到的方向发展……！？

靠着智慧与机智动摇世界局势，
天才王子的弱小国家经营故事，就此开幕！

playlists.title: 自称贤者弟子的贤者 [中字]
playlists.description:
有着无限可能性的“VRMMO-RPG“Ark Earth Online ”

由玩家建立的国家阿尔凯特王国的九贤者之一，充满威严的年老召唤术士邓不利夫也是玩家之一。
某一天，他发现世界出现异常变化。

出现了原本在游戏里没有的味觉及嗅觉，也无法登出。
而且NPC还出现了非常有人味的反应。
这完全就是游戏确切化为现实的证明。
更夸张的是在这个世界已经经过了30年的岁月。

其中最不得了的，就是邓不利夫由于各种情况变成了年幼又美丽的少女模样！
为了解开世界突然改变的谜团，邓不利夫自称是贤者的弟子米菈展开旅行。

而在冒险的终点等着她的究竟是——
