playlists.title: Sabikui Bisco [English Sub]
playlists.description: Japan, where the "Rusty Wind" that rusts away everything is blowing violently. People have been living while being afraid of the rust, which invades the town and threatens peoples’ lives. Bisco Akaboshi is a young man of the Mushroom Guardians, which is a tribe that people hate. To save his dying master, he goes on a journey to find "Rust Eater" mushroom, the miracle medicine that purifies all rust. During his journey, he meets a beautiful young man Milo Nekoyanagi in Imihama, who’s a doctor. Milo is also looking for a way to save his dear older sister from the rust. To save the ones they love, these two boys join hands to start their new adventure.

playlists.title: Teasing Master Takagi-San S3 [English Sub]
playlists.description: Currently being serialized in Monthly Shōnen Sunday(Shogakukan), a coming-of-age comedy that has sold over 10 million copies in total! Through teasing, the distance between the two gets closer. In 2022, this will be the story of ‘first love’ that you will want to watch over! At a certain middle school, a boy named Nishikata is always teased by the girl sitting next to him, Takagi-san. Nishikata tries his best to tease her back, but she always sees right through him instead. Every day, Nishikata struggles hard to find a way to catch Takagi-san off-guard and embarrass her. Yet as the days go by, not only do the seasons change, but Nishikata as well...? On the other hand, Takagi-san, who always had the upper hand, slowly seems wavering…? Will love be shown, or will love be found out? Filled 100% to the brim with heart-pounding grins, the teasing battle finally enters its last round!

playlists.description:
“桃源乡”，一个人与妖怪、科学与妖术共存的
无秩序却安稳的大陆。
但在牛魔王复活实验发出的负面波动的影响下，
妖怪们突然失控，破坏了这块净土的平衡。
天界的观世音菩萨遂命令玄奘三藏阻止牛魔王复活实验，
三藏于是带着孙悟空、沙悟净、猪八戒朝西域天竺前进。
三藏等人在旅途中抵达的城镇，
邂逅拥有起死回生法术的
灰杰尔・葛罗斯，以及随从卡特。
从西域前来的灰杰尔有何目的呢——

playlists.title: 少女前线 [中字]
playlists.description:
2045年，全世界遭受坍塌液污染的地球。
围绕着人类最原始的食住的需求，爆发了卷入全世界的第三次世界大战。
终战后的世界已经一片荒芜。
在文明被逼至毁灭边缘的同时，伴随战争以及其导致的劳动力不足，促使了机械技术的进步，结果创造出了模仿人类的“人形”。
其目的是为人类提供各种服务，外表虽和人类的少女如出一辙，但是有着远超人类能力的机械生命体。那便是“人形”。
然后随着技术进一步的发展，让人形拿上配对枪械的“战术人形”被各种军事组织采用。
其中的军事工业“铁血工造”的AI突然对人类掀起反叛，试图调查并将其阻止的民间军事公司“格里芬”的战术人形与对方拉开了战斗的序幕。
由隶属于“格里芬”的最高级战术人形组成的“AR小队”成员，在与人类指挥官一同取回各地秩序、守护人类安全的同时，也将解开潜藏于战争背后的巨大谜团。
由战术人形们交织的壮烈战斗，在尽头究竟有什么在等待着…。

playlists.title: Girls’ Frontline [English Sub]
playlists.description: The year is 2045, and the entire world has been contaminated by the Collapse Fluid. With the rise of conflicts concerning the most basic of human needs with shelter and foods, the Third World War erupted. What's left after the war is but a world in ruins. As civilisation is pushed to the brink of destruction, both war and the dwindling number of manpower has stimulated the advancement of machine technology, which resulted in the creation of "Dolls" that are created in the image of the humans. As they are manufactured in order to provide all kinds of service to humans, these dolls do not look any different from any normal human girls. However, they are a machine lifeform with abilities far surpassing any human. Those are what these "Dolls" are. As technology progresses even further, many military organizations started using Dolls that are uniquely matched with firearms, called "Tactical Dolls". Amidst all of this, the AI of the weapon manufacturing company "Sangvis Ferri" started a revolt against mankind. The PMC "Griffin & Kryuger" is ordered to investigate and stop them, and thus a battle awaits the Griffin T-Dolls. Within the G&K is a group of the most advanced T-Dolls, called the "AR Team", and along with a human commander of G&K, they will attempt to restore order to various regions, protect the safety of mankind, while also exposing the grand mystery that lies behind their fights. What awaits at the end of their fierce battle...?

playlists.title: 秘密内幕-女警的反击 [中字]
playlists.description:
“警察这种工作，我做不下去了啦！”
挑战过每一种公务员考试，录取的就只有警察而已。
因为在所有想得到的当中最肤浅的理由而成为警察的川合麻依后悔不已。
早知道工作量这么大又容易惹人厌，就绝对不会当警察！
就在川合手中紧握着辞呈，决定要步上第二段事业人生时，
前来担任她新的指导员的人，是以首席的成绩从警察学校毕业，
人称“完美小姐”的前刑事课王牌．藤圣子。
川合听闻藤因为对后辈职场霸凌，
才会从刑事课被调职到派出所的谣传而感到害怕，
却立刻就要跟她搭档前去巡逻……
菜鸟警察．川合跟前刑事课王牌．藤的凹凸搭档为中心，
由个性鲜明又各有魅力的警察们掀起的
有欢笑、有惊吓，有时还有感人泪水的职场喜剧在此揭开序幕！
临场吧！这就是真实（？）又新颖的派出所女子故事！

playlists.title: Police in a Pod [English Sub]
playlists.description: "I had enough of this job!" After taking every single civil service exam, the only one Mai Kawai passed was one for police office work. She took the job without much thought, but it didn't take long for her to regret her decision. If she knew how exhausting the work is and how much she'd be hated for it, she would've never become a police officer. Kawai was so ready to hand out her letter of resignation and move on to her second life. But everything changes when a new director comes as her instructor. Coming to her station is "Miss Perfect" Seiko Fuji, a valedictorian from the police academy and former ace of the criminal affairs division. The rumor says that Fuji got transferred because she often used her authority to abuse younger detectives. But without even a minute of rest, Kawai immediately stuck patrolling with her. The is the beginning of office work comedy full of laughter and surprise, with a sprinkle of tears revolving around the new police officer Kawai and former ace of the criminal affairs division Fuji, along with their unique and charming police officer friends. Attendance! Here we present to you the realistic(?) tale of a new police in a pod!

playlists.title: Death March to The Parallel World Rhapsody [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Ichiro "Satwo" Suzuki is a game programmer in the middle of a death march. When he was taking a nap during his shift, he found himself in another world. Out of the corner of his eye, he sees a menu screen reminiscent of the game he was working on before his nap. He starts out as a Level 1 player, but also equipped with Map Reveal and Meteor Shower x3 skills, which were just implemented to help new players. While he is busy grasping the new reality before him, a huge army of lizards marches before him! In order to save his life, Satwo uses the Meteor Shower, which gives him a level boost up to Level 310 and a huge amount of treasure.
Be this a dream or reality, Satwo's journey in the new world begins!

playlists.title: 出租女友 [中字]
playlists.description:
20岁的废柴大学生，木之下和也。
与人生第一位女友仅接过一次吻、短短一个月就被甩了。

“啊啊…已经…怎样都好了…”

和也自我放弃夏，凭着“某个方法”成功与女孩子约上会。
前往会面场所后

“你就是和也，对吧”

滑顺的黑发，将头发拨上耳际的动作，
温柔看向和也的美少女，水原千鹤露出了微笑

仅此一次的"租借"之中
一定也有绚烂的"真实"

恋爱X心跳MAX的混乱恋爱故事、开幕！

playlists.title: 同居人是貓 [中字]
playlists.description:
不善常与人相处、怕生内向的小说家．朏(音读:翡)素晴，与被人丢弃后、靠自己一路活过来的一只野猫。
因为一个小小的契机开始生活的一人一猫，究竟会度过怎样的日子呢…?
以人与猫两种视角，来描绘平凡日常中对彼此的想法，进而交织成令人感到暖心不已的故事。
累积着点点滴滴的共处时间，我们渐渐成为“家人”－－
一起找到的幸福生活就在这里。

playlists.title: My Roommate is a Cat [English Sub]
playlists.description: Mystery author Mikazuki would rather live in total isolation than deal with others. Getting a roommate is the last thing he’d ever do, until a stray cat sparks an idea for his next novel. After plucking the little killer off the streets, this four-legged muse inspires Mikazuki in ways he would have never expected. And for the street-wise cat, this human just opened the door to a whole new world.

playlists.title: JOJO的奇妙冒险 第三季(不灭钻石) 【中字】
playlists.description: 在埃及跟死敌迪奥(DIO)决一死战之后，过了11年。1999年空条承太郎为了寻找外公乔瑟夫．乔斯达的私生子东方仗助，来到了日本M县S市的社王町。但承太郎所找到的仗助，有与他相同的特殊能力，就是拥有“替身”。然而，随着承太郎的来访，简直就像是互相吸引一样，新的“替身使者”们也开始展开行动。“这座小镇隐藏着秘密……”为了守护自己生长的杜王町，仗助挺身而出──。

In 1999, Jotaro Kujo went to Morioh in S City in M Prefecture, Japan, to find his grandfather, Joseph Joestar's secret child, Josuke Higashikata. However, Josuke had the same ability as Jotaro, the Stand. And as though Jotaro was summoning them, a new group of Stand Users start to make their moves. There's something in this town... Josuke rises up to save Morioh, his hometown that he grew up in.

playlists.title: This Art Club Has a Problem  [English Sub]
playlists.description:
This is this season's most fun youth love comedy in culture club!
In a normal learning institution with nothing out of the ordinary, Tsukimori Middle School, there is a normal art club.
In that club, there are Uchimaki Subaru, a boy who even if he has a lot of talent is all bent on creating his ideal "2D Wife", and Usami Mizuki, who likes such hopeless Uchimaki.
Also, there are the always sleeping President, who seemed to not mind the two of them but actually does, and the puzzling member Colette, whose only point is the somewhat strong presence.
And so, today too, some kind of problem ensues to the Art club, where those slightly sad group of people.

playlists.title: Taisho Otome Fairytale [English Sub]
playlists.description:
The time is of the Taisho period (AD 1912-1926).

Shima Tamahiko was born into a wealthy family and grew up without ever encountering any serious problem. Yet one day, a tragic incident caused him to lose his right hand’s function, his father’s hope in him, and his mother.

Under the pretence of rehabilitation, he was sent off to the countryside, where he grew into a pessimist that loathes everything in the world.

It was then when a girl named Yuzuki came to him.
She is assigned by Tamahiko’s father to care for him, as his bride.

At first, Tamahiko finds Yuzuki annoying, but gradually, her smile and kindness start to open his heart...

Will they get along and become a true husband and wife?
And so, the curtain opens on the nostalgic Taisho love story.

playlists.title: 逆转世界的电池少女 [中字]
playlists.description: 西元2019年，正当日本即将更改年号之际，上空突然出现了异次元的裂缝。存在于那里的是天地逆转的异世界“真国日本”。这个维持着过去的军国主义、始终都是昭和年代的平行世界，透过让现有兵器无效化的气体兵器“幻雾”和巨大人形兵器“伽蓝”对我们的日本发动了军事侵略。他们转眼间掌握了政权，并在完成了实质上的征服。结果我们并未迎来“令和”的年代……。───在那之后又过了十年。日本如今变成了真国的附属国“幻国・日本”。因为严格的审查，使得过去鼎盛的漫画、漫画、偶像等次文化完全消失灭绝……乍看之下似乎是如此。但是，Otaku is not dead！有一个为了守护次文化挺身对抗真国的集团。他们的名字是秘密结社“荒霸吐”。他们的主力兵器是“伽蓝人偶”，以及做为其动力源战斗的少女们。人们是如此称呼她们的…“电池少女”…。

playlists.title: RUMBLE GARANNDOLL [English Sub]
playlists.description:
The year is 2019, right before Japan changes over to a new era.
A dimensional rift suddenly opens up in the sky.
On the other side lies a topsy-turvy world with an alternate version of Japan called "Shinkoku Nippon." 
In this parallel world, Japan has maintained its former militarism, remaining in an eternal Showa era.
Shinkoku Nippon invaded our Japan, deploying “Genmu,” gas weapons that nullify our modern-day weapons, and giant humanoid weapons called “Garann.” 
In the blink of an eye, the invaders seized control of the government and conquered virtually all of Japan.
And thus, the "Reiwa era" never ushered in.
―――A decade later, Japan has been reborn as Genkoku Nippon, a vassal state of Shinkoku. 
Under harsh censorship, the once-thriving manga, anime, idol, and other subcultures have completely died off... or so it seemed.
However, Otaku culture is not dead!
There exists a group that directly opposes Shinkoku to protect Japan’s subcultures.
The name of this secret society is "Arahabaki." 
Their main weapons are “Garanndolls,” powered and piloted by female warriors.
And these female warriors are known by people as... 
“Battery Girls.”

playlists.title: The World's Finest Assassin Gets Reincarnated in Another World as an Aristocrat [English Sub]
playlists.description:
The world's best assassin was reincarnated into the fantasy world of sword and magic. By the Goddess request, he's planning to assassinate the hero!
Lugh, who was reincarnated as the son of a noble family, using the right that's given from the Goddess to him, he got 5 skills, and affinity with magic. Together with his experience from his previous life, he trains himself and grows to become the best asassin in the other world.
Lugh who got his hands on magic, and excelled on martial arts, met with girls who have magic powers, and he raised them to becom an assassin partner. As a preparation for the day they assassinate the hero.
Lugh was frustrated with how the organization he worked with threw him away as if he's just a tool, in his previous life.
In his new, reincarnated life, he decided to stop listening to orders, and live according to his own will.
And then, for the sake of that freedom, he just needs to do one duty, it's to carry on the hero's assassination!

playlists.description: 于每年夏天举办，对目标成为偶像的少女们来说最大的成名途径──“SELECTION PROJECT”对所有努力想成为偶像的少女来说，那是她们毕生憧憬的舞台。同时也是传说中的偶像“天泽灯”诞生的地方。美山铃音也是其中一位，对那座梦幻舞台怀抱憧憬的人。自幼体弱多病的她，曾躺在病床上听了无数次灯演唱的歌曲。灯的歌声给了她无数的笑容与勇气。能成为他人精神支柱的歌声、能使他人绽放笑容的歌声、能让人感受到幸福的歌声……“我想成为像灯那样的偶像。”国中最后一年的夏天，铃音为了实现自己的梦想，决定报名参加第七届的“SELECTION PROJECT”。前往挑战SELECTION的少女们，各个有着不输给任何人的强韧心智、付出汗水累积而来的实力，以及独特的非凡魅力。即便如此，能从数千候补中脱颖而出的明日之星只有少数几人。现在，为了实现自身梦想，少女们即将展开一场残酷的激烈战斗──

playlists.title: SELECTION PROJECT  [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Held every summer, the national idol audition reality show "SELECTION PROJECT" is said to be the biggest gateway to success for aspiring idols.
This year marks the seventh season of the show, and the girls who have won the auditions have all made spectacular debuts, gaining popularity both in the country and abroad.
The reality show follows the girls who have won the nine regional auditions in Hokkaido, Tohoku, Northern Kanto, Southern Kanto, Kinki, Chubu, Chugoku, Shikoku and Kyushu-Okinawa through documentary footage and live show streaming as they challenge the main audition.
The only way to decide who will win is through the votes of the viewers watching the show. Who will win the audition and be crowned as the Debut Idol with the most votes?
The girls are friends and rivals in the battle for the same dream, and now the curtain rises on their youthful, passionate audition battle!

After dying of overwork in the real world, I’m reincarnated as an immortal witch, and I spend 300 years enjoying a relaxing life. At some point, though, I end up at level 99!

playlists.title: The Helpful Fox Senko-san [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Nakano, a salaryman going back and forth from his apartment to an exploitative company, is suddenly visited by a 800-year-old demi-fox taking the appearance of a young girl, Senko.
She "takes care" of the exhausted Nakano by making him food, doing his laundry, and other "special services"(?) to keep him rejuvenated. With Nakano's daily life drastically changing with Senko by his side, a comedic, pampering story for those tired with modern society begins!

playlists.title: JoJo's Bizarre Adventure (Season 4): Golden Wind [English Sub]
playlists.description: Giorno Giovanna is a young man that lives in Naples and is the son of DIO, the nemesis of the Joestar family. When he was younger, he was oppressed and started acting out, but one day, he saved a gang member and then learned how to trust people. Bizarrely, he never forgot that and learned how to be respectful with  his own gang that straightened him out. That’s also how he started aspiring to become a Gang-Star. Now fifteen, Giorno gets in trouble with the gang Passione, which controls the Italian mafia underworld, and now, he’s being targeted.

playlists.title: 恋爱与谎言 [中字]
playlists.description: 政府通知，一到十六岁时便会接到来自政府的结婚对象通知。而有天，我们被通知“恋爱”了。“谎言”不被允许。“恋爱”更是禁忌。一到十六岁时便由政府通知结婚对象的超・少子化对策基本法，通称结缘法。不用费心寻找另一半，所有人都接受由国家保证是天生一对的“幸福”。在这样的世界里，十五岁的主人公・根岛由佳吏，却喜欢着班上的高岭之花・高崎美咲。根岛由佳吏在十六岁生日前夜，终于下定决心要将自己埋藏多年心意传达给某人。但就在同一时间，政府通知送到他的手中。透过科学的红线结合的对象是…。“必须去喜欢的人” “不可以喜欢上的人”全由政府独断决定的世界。究竟是希望还是绝望…少男少女们专一而纯粹的心意交织而成的青涩梦幻禁忌恋爱物语。

playlists.title: (Available until 30th June 2022) Love and Lies [English Sub]
playlists.description:
"Falling in love with someone" - Do people fall into that trap without realizing it? In a near-future world where marriage partners are assigned by the government, it gives hope as well as despair. An ordinary girl, Aoi, receives a notice from the government, which assigns her to marry a random but genetically perfect boy, Sosuke.
However, she realizes she has special feeling toward her childhood friend, Yuto.
In a world where love is not free will, Aoi struggles between Sosuke and Yuto.

playlists.title: Phantom in the Twilight [English Sub]
playlists.description:
A fantasy tale of the girl who defies fate and the “Keeper of Shadow”.
A young girl, Baileu Ton, was caught up in a mysterious incident as soon as she arrived in England.
As if being led in, she wandered into Café Forbidden, which secretly opened at midnight.
The store was surprisingly staffed by a vampire named Vlad, a werewolf named Luke, a Jiangshi named Tauryuu, and Wayne, who calls himself a ghost…
Yes, they were those what is often called “Non-human”. Moreover, these four were actually members of a secret organization working on “certain specialized cases”!
Around Ton, the quiet night of London dramatically changed. This is an unusual fantasy were many different ideas intertwined.

playlists.description: 现在正值樱花开始飘落的春天。个性天真烂漫的小国公主．莉欧，即将进入北海道的学校就读。那里是为了培育守护世界和平的“定理者”、由阿尔卡负责营运的特殊教育机构。在莉欧所就读的一年S班上，以定理者妮娜为首，有许多充满个性的同学。定理者的雏型们一同度过的，充满喧闹又可爱的日子——合体即将开始！

playlists.title: Hina Logic [English Sub]
playlists.description: On a spring day when the cherry blossoms have started to fall, the naïve princess of a small country, Lion begins her days at a school in Hokkaido. The school houses a special facility run by ALCA that trains Logicalists who protect the peace of the world. Lion has a lot of unique classmates in Class 1-S, including Nina, a Logicalist. This is the story of the energetic and adorable days the Logicalists-in-training spend together. It’s time to Trance!

playlists.title: Luck & Logic [中字]
playlists.description: L.C.922年，人类面临了空前的危机。神话世界“泰德拉海文”的百年战争结束后，战败的魔神们为了寻求新的安居之地，前来袭击人界“瑟谱多毗亚”。隶属于警察特殊机构阿尔卡(ALCA)的年轻定理者们，背负着从异世界的使者手中守护城镇的宿命，无论他们是否希望，政府都强制他们接受守护城镇居民的使命，他们藉着特殊能力与异世界的女神们合体，投身战场。某个缺乏“逻辑”，却与家人过着幸福生活的平民——剑美亲，某一天人们受到魔神袭击而拼命逃亡，在那当中他遇到了美丽的女神雅典娜。她拥有美亲原本已经失去的“逻辑”。于是，美亲与雅典娜一同被引向出乎预料的命运。世界的未来，已交托给年轻的定理者们天生的“运气(luck)”与“逻辑(logic)”。

playlists.title: Luck & Logic [English Sub]
playlists.description: In the year L.C.922, the demonic lords of Tetra-Heaven, the world of mythology, arrived at Septpia, the world of humans. The young logicalists belonging to the special police system ALCA, in order to protect the city and its people, "tranced" (combined) with goddesses of another world to throw themselves into the battlefield. Yoshichika Tsurugi, a civilian that led a happy life despite lacking a certain "logic", meets the beautiful goddess Athena one day and is led into an unexpected destiny. The future of the world was entrusted into the "luck" and "logic" of the young logicalists...

playlists.title: Girlfriend, Girlfriend [English Sub]
playlists.description:
The main character is Naoya, a first-year high school student.
He has just confessed his feelings to Saki--the childhood friend he had been crushing on for a long time.
Now that Saki is finally his girlfriend, Naoya is at the peak of his happiness.

However, suddenly there's a girl named Nagisa who calls out to Naoya.
She wants to be Naoya's girlfriend too.

As Naoya's heart is being swayed by a good girl like Nagisa, he has to make a decision!

This is a neo-standard romantic comedy that starts with a very unexpected choice!

playlists.title: The Detective is Already Dead [English Sub]
playlists.description:
"You, be my assistant."
The young man who's prone to get mixed up in cases, Kimihiko Kimizuka, became an assistant to a self proclaimed girl detective who's as beautiful as an angel, Siesta, on a plane that's flying 10,000 metres above the ground.
For the sake of fighting the enemy of the world, the two of them spent 3 years going around the world. Their adventures passed by in a blink of an eye, and in the end, they got separated by death.
A year passed since that shocking day. Kimizuka who turned into a third grade highschooler, got immersed in normal lifestyle, and spent his days as a normal highschooler. Suddenly, a client appeared in front of Kimizuka.
Are you the detective?
Triggered with his meeting with his girl classmate, Nagisa Natsunagi, a grand story that connects the past to the present is opening its curtain once again.

playlists.title: ASSASSINATION CLASSROOM [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Season 1
A mysterious creature with the enormous power to disintegrate 70% of the moon suddenly appears and declares that he will destroy Earth by March of next year. 
But until that time, for some reason the creature says that he will teach class 3-E (where misfit students end up) of Kunugigaoka Junior High School in Japan.  
This creature possesses incredible powers that even the army can’t overcome, and leaders around the world are left with no choice but to leave it up to Class E of Kunugigaoka Junior High School to defeat the creature.
Class E’s assignment is to assassinate the mysterious creature = “Koro Sensei” (“korosenai”; cannot kill “Sensei”; teacher) and save the world from complete destruction! And they have to do it before they graduate!!
Despite these unusual circumstances, the students do their best to stay positive and grow and learn. 

Season 2
One day, a massive explosion suddenly vaporizes 70% of the moon.
Following that incident, a mysterious creature comes to a middle school classroom for some reason. It claims credit for the destruction of the moon and promises to do the same to Earth in March of the following year. Even more peculiarly, it becomes the teacher of class 3-E (where misfit students end up) of Kunugigaoka Junior High School. The creature possesses powers beyond human understanding and proves impervious to military attacks. The leaders of every nation entrust the alien’s assassination to the students of class 3-E.
The supposedly slow learners of the class are now in an “assassination classroom.” Through new experiences, they forge friendships and gain confidence in themselves.
As the second semester begins, the students feel the pressure of a literal deadline. Will their mission to assassinate the homeroom teacher succeed by graduation?!

playlists.title: Classroom of the Elite [English Sub] | S2 starting from 4th July 2022 at 21:00 (GMT+8)
playlists.description:
On the surface, Tokyo Metropolitan Advanced Nurturing High School is a utopia. The students enjoy an unparalleled amount of freedom, and it is ranked highly in Japan. However, the reality is less than ideal. Four classes, A through D, are ranked in order of their proficiency, and only the top classes receive favorable treatment.

Kiyotaka Ayanokoji is a student of Class D, where the school dumps its worst. There he meets the unsociable Suzune Horikita, who believes she was placed in Class D by mistake and desires to climb all the way to Class A, and the seemingly amicable class idol Kikyo Kushida, whose aim is to make as many friends as possible.

While class membership is permanent, class rankings are not; students in lower ranked classes can rise in rankings if they score better than those in the top ones. Additionally, in Class D, there are no bars on what methods can be used to get ahead. In this cutthroat school, can they prevail against the odds and reach the top?

playlists.title: 欢迎来到实力至上主义的教室 [中字]
playlists.description:
这个社会是否平等？何谓真正的“实力”？
东京都的高度养成高中，那是一所彻底标榜实力至上，号称升学率、就业率百分之百的学校。然而，入学被分到1年D班的绫小路清隆，但学校的作风与实力至上主义的招牌完全相反，只发生与十万圆现金等值的点数给学生，在课业或生活态度上，完全采取放任主义。
班上的同学在梦幻般的高中生活中，过着不断散财、自甘堕落的日子，但是，没多久就发现学校系统机制的真相，而被打入绝望的深渊……！
D班聚集了一堆成绩落后的学生，这些少男少女最后找到的答案是什么呢？是世界的矛盾吗？还是正当的实力社会？

playlists.title: What do you do at the end of the world? Are you busy? Will you save us? [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Willem, the last surviving human, now lives on floating islands among other races, away from the surface that is now inhabited by vicious creatures known as “Beasts”. After a chance encounter with a certain girl, Willem was tasked with managing a certain “weapon warehouse”, but to his surprise, the place is more like a dorm full of young girls, with the girl she met before among them. In truth, they are the “Fairy soldiers”, a short-lived race that are tasked to sacrifice their live fighting the Beasts.

"If I'm going to die in five days, would you be a little bit nicer to me?"

playlists.title: 末日时在做什么？有没有空？可以来拯救吗？ [中字]
playlists.description:
这是被称之为妖精兵器的少女们，
以及残存下来的准勇者之间虚幻而悲伤的故事。


这里是地上遭受到不明的怪物“兽”的蹂躏、包含人类在内的许多种族灭亡后的世界。
勉强幸存下来的种族离开地面，来到了被称之为浮游大陆群、漂浮在空中的群岛上生活。
500年后，威廉·克梅修在空中苏醒过来了。
威廉因为自己不但没能守护想要守护的事物，甚至还独自苟活下来的绝望，而开始过着隐士般的生活。
而他却在意外获得的兵器管理的工作之中，与一群少女们相遇了。

playlists.title: 爱丽丝与藏六 [中字]
playlists.description:
在那之前，她都不知晓“外面的世界”。
初次接触的事物、初次看到的景色，以及初次遇见的人们…。
对于“世界”如此之广阔，她大开眼界，感到困惑又惊奇。

她的名字叫纱名。

在被称之为“研究所”的设施中，
在不曾接触“外面的世界”的状况下被养育长大的少女。
同时，她也是拥有能够将各式各样的想像化为现实—被称之为“爱丽丝之梦”的特殊能力的能力者。

第一次来到“外面”后，她与一位老人相遇了。
他的名字叫樫村藏六。
个性“讨厌拐弯抹角”，坚持“不对的事就是不对”的顽固老爷爷。
与藏六的相遇，使得纱名的命运产生了巨大的变化。

追赶纱名的神秘组织、接二连三现身的能力者们、以及与心地温柔善良的人们的相遇…。
不食人间烟火的爱丽丝穿越了镜之门，了解到这世界真实的面貌。

——没错，这是…我还能够自由自在地前往梦之国时的故事。

playlists.description: 在位于釜谷市的“天万神社”，有一位兼职巫女工作的国中二年级生．皇缠。从小就与母亲分开的她，长年以来都被寄养在父方的祖父母家中，直到三个月前才终于开始和父亲伸吾两人一起生活。或许是因为有这样的境遇，她十分向往平凡安稳的日常生活。小缠的好友，同时也是打工同伴的草薙由麻，是出身于天万神社神主一族的下一期巫女候补。她得知了她们一族的祖先世世代代都在进行驱除恶灵的“退魔行”，于是想邀请小缠挑战“退魔行”的仪式“神悬之仪”。学校放学后，两人一如往常地来到了神社，看到的却是乱成一团的神社以及由麻受伤倒下的父母。此外，刑警伸吾正在做调查的某个怪异事件的重要关系人，一个氛围异常的男人也出现在现场。为了压制住那个男人，由麻立刻进行了“神悬之仪”，然而发生异变的人却不是由麻──。追求普通的平凡生活的少女被授予的，竟然是被神明附身驱逐恶灵的能力！？为了取回不受任何人干扰的平稳生活，皇缠开始努力展开退活（退魔活动）！

There were heroes who saved the world in the past. 
Many heroes fought the forces of “Destruction” and protected this world.

playlists.title: Tokyo Revengers [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Takemichi Hanagaki is a part-time timer whose life is at rock bottom.
Later he learns that the only girlfriend he ever had in his life whom he dated back in middle school, Hinata Tachibana had been killed by the "Tokyo Manji Gang," a group of vicious criminals.
The day after he learned about the incident, Takemichi's standing on a station platform and got his back pushed onto the railroad by someone. Thinking he would die from the fall, he closes his eyes. However, when he opens it back, he somehow finds himself traveled back tweleve years into the past.
Now that he returned to the peak of his life, the middle school days twelve years ago, in order to save his girlfriend, in order to change himself who had been running away all these time, Takemichi started his Revenge on his life!

playlists.description:
花垣武道是个生活潦倒的打工仔，有天，他得知国中时交往的唯一一个女友橘日向，遭罪凶恶的恶党组织“东京卍会”杀害。得知事件的隔天，人站在车站的武道被某个人推落月台，就在他做好当场毙命的觉悟时，不知为何，睁眼后却发现自己穿越到了12年前。

playlists.title: The Saintʼs Magic Power is Omnipotent [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Sei is a somewhat workaholic office lady in her twenties.
As she returns home after another night of overtime work, she is suddenly enveloped in light and is summoned into another world as a “Saint”. There is another girl that is also summoned together with her, a high-school girl.
A prince who appears is immediately preoccupied with the other girl and totally ignores Kei.
“Fine, I’m free to do whatever I want, right?”
As she said that, Sei leaves the royal palace. Making use of her natural love of plants, Sei started working at a medicinal plant research institute as a civilian.
With the help of Johan, the director, and Jude, the education officer, Sei starts to learn how to use magic and create potions. However, it turns out that everything Sei makes is 50% more potent, unexpectedly showing her ability as a Saint.
When Sei’s potion saved the life of Albert, a dying knight commander, rumors begins to circulate that Sei was the true Saint...

playlists.title: 圣女魔力无所不能 [中字]
playlists.description: 圣是个有些沉迷工作的二十几岁上班族，这天晚上她加班回家，突然被一阵光包围，结果以“圣女”的身分，被召唤到异世界去了。而且被召唤的人居然有两个人!?出现在眼前的王子只顾着搭理另一位女高中生，完全无视圣。“既然这样，那我可以照我的意思做吧？”说完，圣飞奔出王宫。她活用自己原本就喜欢植物这点，进入药用植物研究所，以普通人的身分开始工作。她受到约翰所长和裘德前辈的帮助，慢慢学习制作药水和使用魔力。但她做出来的东西，效果都比别人多出五成，原来她在不知不觉间，发挥了“圣女”的能力。这时候，圣的药水救了濒死状态的骑士团长——艾尔伯特的性命。此后，人们开始低声私语，说圣会不会才是真正的“圣女”⋯⋯!?

The infamous giant corporation, a self proclaimed evil organisation that has done many nefarious deeds, has defeated the heroes and is finally close to achieving world domination.

This restructuring problem has to be solved,

playlists.title: Osamake: Romcom Where The Childhood Friend Won't Lose [English Sub]
playlists.description:
She would smile at me, and only me.
The person is Kachi Shirokusa, a very beautiful high school writer who won the Akutami Award!
And I, Maru Sueharu is just a normal high school boy. She and I are not a match in the slightest!
But I think I got a chance with her... maybe, no, definitely!
...That what I thought at first, but... you're telling me she already has a boyfriend?!
Right when I was depressed, someone came up to me. She's small, cute, and caring. Not to mention, she somehow told me that she likes me. She's my childhood friend, Shida Kuroha. And then she says...
"Let's have revenge"
The grudge of first love is deeper than the sea--- however, it's not dark! It's not muddy!
My first love revenge now begins!

对方是得到芥见赏的现役女高中生作业可知白草！而且还是美少女！
我丸末晴也知道身为普通高中生的自己配不上她！
但是，我觉得自己应该……不，是绝对有机会！
……才刚这么觉得……就发现可知其实有男朋友!?
稚嫩可爱个性开朗又喜欢照顾人，而且不知为何公开表示喜欢我的青梅竹马，对失落的我表示……
“来复仇吧！”
初恋的仇恨比大海更深——但是绝不阴沉！更不惊恐！
初恋复仇就此展开！

Yoshida is an ordinary guy who was rejected hard by the woman he’d spent the last 5 years having a crush on. On his way home after getting drunk at a bar, he finds a teenage girl crouched on the side of the road...
“If you let me stay at your place, you can sleep with me.”
“You shouldn’t say that, even as a joke.”
“Then let me stay over for free.”
Before he knows it, the girl, Sayu, has moved in with him.
This is the story of a runaway teen girl and an ordinary 26-year old man.

playlists.title: ZOMBIE LAND SAGA REVENGE [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Legendary girls beyond space and time are revived as zombies and become an idol save Saga Prefecture.
"A new, sensational zombie idol-type anime"

One morning, Sakura Minamoto died in an accident.
Ten years later...
Sakura wakes up in a certain western-style house and is told by a mysterious idol producer named Kotaro Tatsumi to "become an idol with the other legendary girls and save Saga Prefecture.” As an idol group called Franchouchou, seven zombie girls pave their way to save the prefecture by doing various idol activities. However, nothing is without challenges as an idol’s existence is always as fickle as a candle. As they overcome one trouble after another due to their differences in age and generation, Franchouchou starts overturning the common sense of “idols” with their immortal bodies.
In Heisei era's last winter, Franchouchou succeeded in their first solo live concert at Karatsu City Furusato Hall Arpino and took a step forward to creating their legend. 

And then, in this Reiwa era...
Zombie Land Saga: Revenge offers a new story full of hope as Franchouchou heads to the next stage and an even brighter future.

playlists.title: 佐贺偶像是传奇 卷土重来 [中字]
playlists.description:
某天早上，源樱因为遭遇意外事故而断送了生命。
10年后──
樱在某栋洋房醒来后，眼前的神秘偶像制作人・巽幸太郎向她表示“你要和传说中的少女们一起成为偶像拯救佐贺！”。由七名少女组成的偶像团体“法兰秀秀”为了拯救存在已有如风中残烛的佐贺县而开始展开活动。
她们一路克服年龄及时代的差异所发生的各种问题，并以丧尸的不死之躯不断颠覆偶像的常识。然后，她们在平成最后的冬天，在唐津市乡土会馆举行了第一次的独立演唱会并获得了大成功，朝向传说跨出了新的一步。
然后，在这令和时代，
朝着充满希望的闪耀未来向前迈进，法兰秀秀崭新的故事即将揭开序幕。

playlists.title: Hand Shakers [中字]
playlists.description:
握手者－－
那是两人双手相系，
以诞生自深层心理的武器"宁录"彼此战斗的人们。
为了实现自己的“愿望”，必须谒见"神"，击败"神"，
众多的握手者们以那巅峰为目标互相竞争。
于斗争的尽头，存在的事物是－－。


──osaka
擅长操弄机械的高中生手纲，接到一桩修理的委托造访了大学的研究室。
他在那里遇见在床上沉睡的一名少女小代理。
仿佛冥冥中受到指引，手纲碰触了小代理的指尖，
不知来自何方的声音从天而降。

──克服重重战斗、试炼之人。
受到启示之人。
要谒见我、挑战我之人。
即为"握手者"──
手纲为展现在眼前的异样世界"金字型神塔"感到不知所措。
转眼间，手纲与小代理便遭到某人袭击－－。
要谒见神的众多握手者，阻挡在手纲跟小代理的面前。
赌上他们各自的“愿望”……。
用我的手，守护住。

playlists.title: Hand Shakers [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Handshakers, by holding hands, they gave birth to weapons from the depths of their heart.
They fight while holding Nimrod in their hands.
To have your wish granted, you have to meet Gods,
And to defeat the Gods, to stand on that place, is what Handshakers aim for, and what lies beyond it, is...

Osaka, the high school student who's good at fixing machines, Takatsuki Tazuna.
One day, he received a request for repair from a laboratory in unniversity branch.
There, he met with a girl who keeps on sleeping on a bed, Koyori.
As if guided by something, Koyori fingertips touched Tazuna, and a voice start to call upon him. 
You who have been through countless battles, and surpassed trials. 
Who received the revelation.
Who came to us, and challenged us.
You're a Handshaker.
Tazuna was confused when faced upon the parallel world that opened up  right in front of his eyes, the Ziggurat.
In a moment, Tazuna and Koyori received attacks from someone.
To meet the Gods, a number of Handshakers appear in front of Tazuna and Koyori.
While putting their own wish on the line.

playlists.title: 🤩Available again🤩 Rage of Bahamut GENESIS [English Sub]
playlists.description:
This is the magical world of Mistarcia, where humans, Gods, demons, and many different race exist together.
In the past, the silver winged Bahamut drove the world to brink of destruction,
But, humans, Gods, and demons overcame their differences, and cooperated together.
After paying a huge sacrifice, they managed to seal its power.
And then, the key for the seal was separated into two, the God key, and the demon key, both exist within their respective race.
To make sure that the key won't be able to unite again.
After that, 2000 or more years passed, and the world is in an age of peace.
And somehow, humans thought that the Bahamut is a unique existance, so they feared and worship it.
One day, the God key which is impossible to steal, was stolen by a lone girl.
The world balance gently starts to crumble.
Once the Bahamut release it's roar of survival, the world will absolutely fall into the depths of despair.
World, perish.
Someone earnestly wish for it.

playlists.title: 巴哈姆特之怒 [中字]
playlists.description:
这里是《人》、《神》、《魔》等各式各样的种族生活的神秘世界“米斯塔希亚”。
过去，有着黑银之翼的巴哈姆特曾让世界几乎濒临毁灭。但是在《人》、《神》、《魔》跨越了种族之间的隔阂共同奋战之下，在付出了惨烈的牺牲后终于将它的力量给封印起来。
然后，封印的钥匙被一分为二，各别交给《神》与《魔》保管，为了永远不让那把钥匙再度合而为一…。

在那之后经过了两千年以上的时间，世界一片祥和，而人类在不知不觉中开始将巴哈姆特视为独一无二的存在畏惧并崇拜它。

就在某一天，绝不可被偷走的“神之钥”被一个少女夺走了。

世界的平衡开始缓慢地步向崩坏。

当巴哈姆特发出复活的咆哮之时，世界将再次陷入绝望的深渊。

“世界，毁灭吧。”
某个人恳切地如此祈望着。

playlists.title: 无畏魔女 [中字]
playlists.description:
1930年代，以欧洲为中心，突然出现人类的敌人“涅洛伊”。一般的武器难以毁坏涅洛伊，能与之对抗的只有──人称“魔女(Witch)”的一群拥有特殊魔力的少女们而已。“勇者魔女”是“强袭魔女”第一期与第二期之间的故事。1944年，以第501统合战斗航空团“强袭魔女”为中心的联合军大显身手，灭掉了位于高卢共和国上空的涅洛伊巢穴，确保了欧洲西部的安全。趁此机会，联合军正式地策划了从欧洲中央往东部的反抗作战计划。并打算命令以欧拉西亚帝国的圣彼得堡为基地的
第502统合战斗航空团“勇者魔女”也一同出击。背负着人类的希望，勇气十足的魔女们，在东欧寒冷的天空中奔驰。

playlists.title: Brave Witches [English Sub]
playlists.description:
1930s, "Neuroi" an enemy of humanity suddenly appeared and attacked Europe.
Normal weapons have trouble dealing with Neuroi.
The only ones able to fight against it are called witches, girls with special magical powers.
Brave Witches is a story that happened between Strike Witches Season 1, and Strike Witches Season 2.
In September 1944, due to the achievements made by the Joint Army centered on 501st Joint Fighter Wing, "Strike Witches", the Neuroi nest on Galia Republic airspace was destroyed, and they obtained peace in western Europe.
Seeing this as an opportunity, the Joint Army started to plan seriously for a counter attack in the center and eastern Europe frontline.
Orussia Empire built a base in Petersburg,
And was planning to issue an order to the 502nd Joint Fighter Wing, "Brave Witches", for a sortie too.
The brave witches are flying across the cold sky of Eastern Europe, while carrying humanity's hope on their back.

画面一转，来到2030年的东京港湾地区，潜入未知兵器‘EX-ARM’交易现场的警察．上园美波和生化机器人．阿尔玛这对搭档，遭受到装备着‘EX-ARM’No.8的敌人袭击。两人为了赌一次起死回生的机会，启动从敌人手中夺得的‘EX-ARM’No.00，却……!?

playlists.title: Mushoku Tensei jobless reincarnation [English Sub]
playlists.description:
"I'm gonna go all out in this isekai!"
A 34-year-old virgin, jobless, shut-in and NEET, male. 
On the day of his parents' funeral, he was kicked out of the house, and then immediately got run over by a truck and lost his life.
To his surprise, when he woke up, he was reincarnated as a baby in an isekai of swords and magic. 
The man who once lived his life like a scum, has now become a boy named Rudeus, and swears that he'll give his best effort into life in this isekai! 
Awaiting Rudeus is a loli magician, 
a pretty girl with elf ears who uses "Boku" to refer to herself,
a violent tsundere Ojou-sama, 
and his encounters with all sorts of other people.
Moreover, he'll be fighting during his harsh adventures.
His new life is getting started!
A fantasy story of "restarting life", now begins!

playlists.title: 无职转生～到了异世界就拿出真本事～ [中字]
playlists.description:
“我要在这个异世界拿出真本事！”
34岁、处男、无职的家里蹲尼特男。
他在双亲葬礼当天被改出家门的瞬间，就因为遭卡车碾过而丧命。
等他重新醒来，发现自己在剑与魔法的异世界转生成了小婴儿！
曾活得跟垃圾一样的男人，发誓要做为少年鲁迪乌斯在异世界认真过活！
等待着鲁迪乌斯的，是与萝莉魔术师、有着妖精耳朵却使用男性化自称的美少女、凶暴傲娇大小姐，以及其他各式各样人物的相遇，以及残酷的冒险与战斗。
全新的人生就此展开！
“人生重来”奇幻故事，现在开幕！

playlists.title: Scar On The Praeter [English Sub]
playlists.description:
As long as we have friends, our youth continues.
We will thread the same path.
And then, we'll become a family.

Tokyo, "Special Dawn District".
The ones who protect this lawless city that's casted away by the government,
Are special people who were blessed with a special tatoo by God, Scard.
Various hardships befalls upon "Helios", "Artemis", and "Security Office".
They intersect with each other, and surpass it.
And somehow, the string that ties them, is not anger and hatred anymore, but trust.
The Scar on the Praeter is the story about them leaving their backs to each other.

playlists.title: 重创的伤口 [中字]
playlists.description:
只要朋友依然存在，青春便不会消逝。
我们奔驰在相同的道路上并肩前行。
因此我们，成为了家人。

东京──“晓特区”。
守护着被国家舍弃、坏法乱纪的三不管地带的，是寄宿着神所封印的纹身者们──Scard。
层出不穷的困难不断袭击“海利欧斯”、“阿提米斯”与“公安特务”，他们彼此冲突碰撞，却也携手共度难关。
不知从何时开始，连系彼此的羁绊不再是仇恨与愤怒，转换为信赖般的关系。
“Praeter之伤”是个能将自己的后背托付给彼此看照，成为朋友的故事。

playlists.description:
The stage sets in a world where guinea pigs became cars.
The car that makes you relax: "Molcar".
Having big round eyes, curvy butts, and speedy limbs, they always explore the world with their innocent faces.
Even during traffic jams, you can be eased just by looking at the butt of that Molcar in front of you.
Even when they cause trouble, their furry cuteness will somehow make you forgive them!?
Surrounded by situations only met by cars, it's a Mol-animation filled with the cure, friendship, adventure, and furry actions!

playlists.description:
故事舞台发生在一个天竺鼠变成车子的世界。
疗愈系的车“天竺鼠车车”。圆滚滚的眼睛和又大又圆的屁股，短短的手脚。常常一脸傻乎乎地四处奔波的天竺鼠车车。即使塞车了，只要看着前面的天竺鼠车车的屁股就能被疗愈，就算制造了一些麻烦，因为毛茸茸太可爱了也能原谅吧？！
以汽车各式各样的情境为中心的疗愈、友情、冒险、乱七八糟的动作戏以及超多天竺鼠的动画！

The I-Chus' struggle to find the answer to this question will be captured in every shining moment of their lives. 

The coming-of-age story, begins now!

playlists.title: 怪物事变 [中字]
playlists.description:
自古以来，名为“怪物”的存在就一直潜伏于世界的阴影中，
在不为人知的状态下与人类进行接触并生活着。
他们多半都适应了人类的世界，融入了社会的生活。
然而到了现代，却传出了越来越多怪物们与人类进行不必要的过度接触的报告。
经营侦探事务所的隐神，为调查那些“怪物”们所引发的其中一起怪奇事件而造访了某个乡下的偏僻村子。然后，他在那里和一位名叫夏羽的少年相遇了──

playlists.title: Dr. Ramune -Mysterious Disease Specialist- [English Sub]
playlists.description:
As long as hearts exist inside people, there will always be those who suffer.
When something "strange" enters their mind, a strange disease will manifest itself in their body.
The illness, which is called a "mystery disease" is unknown to most, but it certainly exists.
There is a doctor and an apprentice who can fight the disease, which modern medicine cannot cure.

His name is Ramune.
He acts freely all the time, is foul-mouthed, and doesn’t even look like a doctor!
However, once he is confronted with the mysterious disease,
he is able to quickly uncover the root cause of his patients' deep-seated distress and cure them.

playlists.title: 怪病医拉姆尼 [中字]
playlists.description:
人类只要有心，便会有人怀有烦恼。
当“怪”入侵，身体便会产生奇妙的症状。
 
被称为“怪病”的病症，尽管无人知晓，
但确实存在于世上。
有名医生跟徒弟一同，
挺身面对现代医学束手无策的那些病症。
 
他的名字叫拉姆尼。
外表看上去一点都不像医生，
无论何时都自由洒脱。
而且还很毒舌。
 
不过，一旦面对怪病，
他会瞬间抓出隐藏在患者心底烦恼的原因并给予治疗。
而且在那之后－－。

playlists.title: 好比是最终迷宫前的少年到新手村生活一般的故事 [中字]
playlists.description:
罗伊德是居住在距离都会十分遥远的某个村子里的少年。
而梦想成为军人的他其实是“村子里最弱的男人”。
虽然身边的村民们都强烈反对他成为军人，
但意志坚定的罗伊德还是踏上了前往王都的旅程。
然而，包含他在内的村民们都不晓得某个重大的事实。
那就是他们全都是过去曾经拯救世界的英雄的后裔，同时所有人全都有着异于常人的力量。
以及，就连“村子里最弱”的罗伊德也都有着超脱常理的强大…


身体能力出类拔萃！
古代魔法样样精通！
甚至就连做家事也都万无一失！

对自己的强大有所误会的村民带来的
无自觉最强奇幻故事，现在揭开序幕！

playlists.title: 天地创造设计部 [中字]
playlists.description:
天地创造是世界万物的起源。
万能之神创造出世间的所有一切。

祂创造了光、水及大地──
接着，祂准备创造居住在其中的生物…那许许多多的动物们──
原本是这么想的，但因为祂觉得麻烦，所以就发包出去了…！？

天地创造社接到了神（客人）要求创造生物的委托。
存在于地表上的生物们都是天地创造社的设计师们创造出来的。

这个生物为什么会是这个模样呢？
这个生物为什么会有这种生态呢？

在生物诞生的幕后，充满了设计师及工程师们为实现神强人所难的要求，透过他们独创的灵感进行创造、有苦恼也有欢喜的故事！

“有趣又能增长知识！”，
引发热烈回响的“创造生物的职场喜剧”，终于要在2021年动画化！

playlists.title: Heaven’s Design Team [English Sub]
playlists.description:
Everything began, with the creation of the world.
The almighty God created everything.
Created light, water, and land.
Then, He tried to make the creatures that lived there--
that's what He thought, but it became bothersome, so He left it to subcontractors!?
Heaven's design company received a request to design creatures from God.
The animals that exist in earth, were designed by the designers from Heaven's design company.
This animal, why is it shaped this way?
This animal, why does it have this ability?
Behind the birth of animals, there's a drama where designers and engineers agonize, and enjoyed making original ideas to keep up with the God's unreasonable requests!
The creature designing job comedy, which gained a lot of response that said it's interesting and useful, is finally being adapted into anime in 2021!

playlists.description:
主角利姆路与因为仰慕他而集结的众多魔物们成立的国家《朱拉．坦派斯特联邦国》，在与邻近国家签订协议、进行交易的过程中，使得“人类与魔物共存的国家”这温柔的理想开始逐渐成形。

利姆路所抱持的，是过去生为人类的史莱姆的自己“对人类的善意”…。
但是这个世界，存在着明确的“对魔物的恶意”。
面对这充满了不合理的现实，利姆路将面临选择。
“不希望失去的东西是什么”──

playlists.title: BanG Dream! 2nd Season [中字]
playlists.description: 向前奔驰吧！最棒的音乐（梦想）！升上高中2年级的香澄一行人，她们的乐团"Poppin'Party"因为忙着学生会、帮忙家里的店、补习班以及打工，5人能聚在一起的时间变少，也一直没办法在乐团的基地"仓库"集合。这时，有1位少女出现在她们的身边─ 崭新的邂逅，永恒不变的羁绊。Afterglow、Pastel＊Palettes、Roselia、Hello, Happy World!也将会登场，个性丰富的乐团成员们，将用闪耀又令人怦然心动的舞台吸引你！“我想…和大家再一次举办演唱会”音乐（梦想）现在即将向前奔驰！

playlists.title: BanG Dream! [中字]
playlists.description: 香澄一直在找寻。找寻着如同小时候仰望星空时所听见的“星之鼓动”一般，闪耀动人又令人怦然心动的事物。在香澄进入高中就读后不久的某一天，她在老旧的当铺仓库与一把“星形的吉他”相遇，并感受到一股前所未有的悸动，长久以来封闭在心中的情感开始奔腾。与和她一样，一直在找寻着能够闪闪发光的舞台的、四位少女一起。即使是一个人无法演奏出的音色，五个人在一起一定就能够办到！一定要在这里，举行演唱会！

Four months have passed since Popipa’s sponsored concert. After a fun filled summer, fall arrives once again. Warehouse-rehearsal, working part time, and student council meetings- Kasumi and the members of Poppin’ Party return to their usual routines… until one day, a certain poster at Live House Galaxy catches their eyes.

Elsewhere, Rokka, continuing the search for her fated band members, receives a special invitation…

The sparkling, heart-pounding stage calls once more!

Together, no dream is out of reach!

It’s hard to reach for the stars when you don’t know what inspires you, but thanks to a chance meeting between Kasumi and a star-shaped guitar, she finally understands her true calling! Kasumi becomes determined to form an all-girl band, and her search leads her to Saya, Arisa, Rimi, and Tae. Featuring live performances by the band Poppin’Party, Kasumi (played by the band’s lead singer, Aimi), prepares to take the stage and make her dreams of stardom come true, no matter the obstacles.

playlists.title: 最游记 RELOAD BLAST [中字]
playlists.description: 人与妖怪、化学与妖术共存，既混乱又安祥的一片大陆——“桃源乡”。然而，因为某个神秘的“变异”，妖怪们受到负面波动影响而失控大闹，使那平衡突然崩解。为了阻止万恶的根源“牛魔王的复活实验”，前往西天的三藏一行人，终于即将抵达天竺，但是越接近天竺，变异的影响也越来越浓烈，战斗慢慢陷入白热化。此外，五百年前哀怨的因果纠缠也阻挡在三藏一行人面前……。

playlists.title: SAIYUKI RELOAD BLAST [English Sub]
playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
Humans and yokai, science and magic... all exist side-by-side on a peaceful continent free of all order and regulation, widely known as "Shangri-La." The balance there was shattered when the Minus Wave caused all the yokai on the continent to rampage, an event known as the "Calamity." Continuing their journey west to stop Gyumaoh's resurrection experiments, the root of all the evil on the continent, the Three Aspects are finally drawing closer to India. But the closer they get, the more pronounced the influence of the Calamity becomes, and the more intense their battles become.

playlists.title: 大贵族 [中字]
playlists.description:
在历经820年的漫长沉睡后苏醒的卡迪斯˙艾特拉马˙迪˙莱杰罗。
他是拥有高贵血统与精神的贵族守护者“NOBLESSE”。

与莱杰罗重逢的忠心执事弗兰克斯坦，为了守护莱杰罗，让他成为自己经营的私立艺兰高中的学生。
之后莱杰罗与学校的同班同学相处，过着简单而安逸的日常生活。

然而安逸的生活却突然结束，莱杰罗等人被激烈动荡的漩涡逐渐吞噬…。

来自神秘组织“UNION”的刺客，企图征服世界，
而身为“NOBLESSE”，他是必须保护“贵族”的影子，
攸关820年漫长沉睡的秘密，将逐渐明朗化…。

为了那些必须保护的人们，莱杰罗不得不使用自己的绝对力量…
自此世界将开始变动。

playlists.title: Noblesse [English Sub]
playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
Cadis Etrama Di Raizel awakens from his 820-years slumber. He's a Noblesse, a pure-blooded Noble and protector of all Nobles.

Upon his awakening, he's reunited with his loyal butler Frankenstein who welcome him as a student in his private school; Ye Ran High School.

From that day on, Raizen lives a peaceful ordinary life along with his newly-found classmates.

However, that peaceful ordinary life suddenly comes to an end as Raizen and his friends got involved in a strange chain of events.

An assassin sent by Union, the secret organization that aims to conquer the world. 
The presence of the Nobles.
Lastly, the secret behind Raizel's 820-years slumber.

In order to protect those he needs to protect, Raizel is forced to use his absolute power...

It is, at that moment, the world began to move―.

playlists.title: 光之战记 [中字]
playlists.description:
在进行迁都计划的瓦海特帝国首都中，有两位少年，
努力经营搬运工工作、个性有点胆小的伊曼诺尔，
和刚加入帝国军成为新人士兵、不谙世事的莱奥卡迪欧，
一边是心想着珍惜的妹妹，一边是想着自己成为士兵后的生活，
两人都在帝都为了未来而努力生活着。
然而另一方面，过去曾使得许多生物消灭的凶暴魔物所释放的灾厄‘光’即将再度降临的预言，使得帝都人心惶惶。
在这样的背景下，伊曼诺尔与莱奥卡迪欧的命运，甚至于帝国的历史，皆因一起偷渡事件，面临了激烈的变化。

playlists.title: MAGATSU WAHRHEIT ZUERST [English Sub]
playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝ 
Two young boys who live in the Wahrheit Empire, where the capital city relocation plan is ongoing--
A timid Immanuel, who works hard at his job as a courier, and Leocadio, a new, naive imperial soldier. 

One works for the sake of his dear younger sister, while the other spends his day envisioning his days as a soldier in the imperial capital.

On the other hand, a prophecy foretold that “Light”, a disaster that once released ferocious beasts and annihilated life from the world, is about to be resurrected, which brings devastation to humanity once more.

Meanwhile, the fates of Immanuel and Leocadio, and the history of the empire, are about to change drastically due to a certain smuggling incident...

playlists.title: 忧国的莫里亚蒂 [中字]
playlists.description:
19世纪末。随着产业革命的发展，英国的实力不断壮大以致繁华至极。
但是在技术的进步及发展的反面，自古扎根的阶级制度，
让不到人口3％的贵族们支配了这个国家。
理所当然地享受着特权的贵族。不知道能不能活到明天的底层阶级。
人们的生活都被束缚在一出生就定下的阶级中。

为了打破这种腐败的阶级制度，建立理想中的国家，
威廉．詹姆斯．莫里亚蒂展开了行动。

就连夏洛克．福尔摩斯也能玩弄于鼓掌之间的“犯罪卿”莫里亚蒂。
靠犯罪造就的革命来改变世界──

playlists.description:
Genre: Mystery, Suspense
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
End of 19th Century. England, whose influence was steadily extending and its prosperity at its peak during the progression of industrial revolution. 
However, contrary to the development of technology, due to the rooted class system since ancient times, the nobles that account for less than 3% of the population were dominating the country.
The nobles enjoyed their privilege for granted, while the underclass had trouble even to live for another day. People’s lives were bound by classes, which were decided when they were born. 
William James Moriarty took actions to destroy such a corrupted class system, and build up an ideal country. 
Moriarty, the criminal who managed to trick even Sherlock Holmes. The revolution caused by crimes, was about to change to world…

“只要有了这个，就算在家也能轻松完成梦寐以求的征服世界！”讲白了就是开发像是“想便便咒语”之类有各式各样效果的咒语，然而却有人连同开发系统全部都偷走了！

playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
The Evil Secret Organization "Eagle Talon" has successfully revived the ancient curse; Golden Spell that allows them to control humans at their will.

"With this, we can finally fulfill our long dream of world conquest from the comfort of our home!" they thought, and successfully created various Golden Spell such as "Bladder Spell". However, someone stole the Spell development program!

If Golden Spell fell on the hand of a person with malice, the world in fall into chaos.

To take back the stolen Spell, the Eagle Talon began an investigation. However, they eventually got dragged into a giant conspiracy...

Protect! The world and Social Distance!

playlists.title: 无能力者娜娜 [中字]
playlists.description:
“我可以读出别人的内心！但是，我不太会看气氛！请多多指教！”

位于孤岛上的神秘学园。出现在中岛七雄面前的是转学生柊娜娜。
这里是聚集了拥有各种能力的少年少女们的设施。
操纵火焰和冰的人。自由地飞舞于空中的人。能将空气化为刀刃攻击的人。
学生们为了和被称为“人类之敌”的怪物战斗而接受训练。
但是，这岛上也隐藏着许多秘密，可怕的陷阱露出了爪牙。
连续发生的奇妙事件。潜藏于学园的杀人魔。一个一个接着消失的同学。
超越预料的展开。倾尽智力、能力的智略战，以及友情。
热血的剧情以及和“人类之敌”死斗，现正开始！

"I can read people's minds. 
But I can't really read the atmosphere.
It's nice to meet you! "

A strange academy on an isolated island in the ocean. In front of student Nakajima Nanao is new transfer student Hiiragi Nana.

This is a place where boys and girls with various abilities gather

A person who manipulates flame and ice. A person who can fly freely in the air. A person who can use air as a blade to attack. 

The students are trained to fight monsters known as the "Enemies of Mankind". 

But there are a number of secrets hidden on the island, and a terrifying trap reveals its fangs.

A series of mysterious incidents....A murderer hidden in the school, classmates who disappears one by one.

A development out of anyone's expectations.  Beyond intellect and capabilities. A battle of brains. And then friendship.

A heated drama, a Battle Royale against Humanity's Enemies is about to begin!

playlists.title: 铁路浪漫谭 [中字]
playlists.description:
正和63年10月。
由于大幅废除而几乎失去了铁路的国家——日本里的九洲，隈元县御一夜市。
为了重整萧条至极的经济，以8620型蒸汽火车以及其人偶・八六为主角所开发的观光振兴计
画顺利成功，并一跃成为铁路复兴圣地的御一夜市，为了寻求更进一步的复兴机会，也为了和
全国的铁路经营者、铁路人偶们有更多交流，决定计划举办‘第一次My铁路祭’。
控制铁路车辆驾驶的人型系统“铁路人偶”们也被各自的所有者从全国各地带到此地。
受到人们连日不断的会议所刺激，产生了“自己也想做点什么”的想法并意气相投的她们，以
著名的铁路人偶“铃城”为首，办起“铁路人偶高峰会”。
她们聚集在车站前的“cafe亚麻色”，为了让“My铁路祭”更加精采而绞尽脑汁。

playlists.title: Rail Romanesque [English Sub]
playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
October, 1988. 
The country has lost most of its railroad tracks due to a huge abolition. Ohitoyoshi, the city in Kumamoto County, Kuzu area. The city became a sacred place for its railway reconstruction, successfully rebuilt its exhausted economy by promoting tourism with steam locomotive 8620 and its Railroads Hachiroku as main features, now plans to hold the First Maitetsu Festival in order to further enhance the city and build up a relationship between the railway operators from all over Japan.
The "Railroads", the humanoid modules for railway car operation and control, will be accompanied by their masters from all over Japan. Inspired by the daily meetings of the humans, they agree immediately to do something together, and organize the "Railroads Summit" led by the famous railroad "Suzusiro". They gather at "Cafe Flaxen" in front of the station and work together to add more color to the "Maitetsu Festival".

playlists.title: 魔女之旅 [中字]
playlists.description:
从前某个地方有一位旅行者，她的名字叫伊蕾娜。
她是位年纪轻轻就成为最高阶魔道士“魔女”的才女。她十分向往小时候看过的旅行故事，目前正顺其自然、随心所欲地进行着漫长的旅程。她自由自在地漫步在这广大的世界，接触了许多叫人摸不着头绪的怪人与陌生人的美妙日常。她身为旅行者并没有明确的目的，不断在旅途中与各式各样的国家与人们相遇。

而有多少次的相遇就会有多少次的——
“请不要在意我，因为我是旅行者。我必须赶路才行。”

这是一段由魔女伊蕾娜所编织的，关于相遇与别离的故事…。

Admiring the stories of travels she read when young, as if being swept away, she continues on her carefree and long travels.

Elaina, a witch like that, spins a tale of encounters and farewells.

playlists.title: Burn the Witch 龙与魔女 [中字]
playlists.description:
世界若存在表（Front）则必然有里（Reverse）。

综观历史的长河，全伦敦总死亡人口数中有72％的死者，与人们所看不到的，被称之为龙的“异常存在”有关。

然而，既然有无法被常人所觉知的龙存在，便有能与之对抗的人们出现。

能看得见龙存在的人，只有居住在表伦敦（Front．London）“内侧”延伸而出的里伦敦（Reverse．London）中的居民。而在他们当中，只有被挑选出的人能成为魔女／魔法师，并获得与龙直接接触的资格。

故事的主角，为自然龙保护管理机关“Wind Bind”（简称ＷＢ）的保护官新桥诺艾儿与妮妮．斯邦柯尔两人所组成的魔女小队。她们两人的使命，是代替无法接触龙的人们，保护并管理生活在伦敦的这些“龙”。

Genre: Action, Fantasy

= TITLE SUMMARY = 

In this world, there is a "FRONT" side and a "REVERSE" side.

Historically 72% of all the deaths in London are related to dragons, fantastical beings invisible to the majority of the people.

While unknown to most, some people have been standing up to these dragons.

Only inhabitants of Reverse London who live in the hidden “reverse” side of London can see the dragons. Even then, only a selected few become qualified enough as witches or wizards to make direct contact with them.

The protagonists of the story are witch duo Noel Niihashi and Ninny Spangcole. They are protection agents for Wing Bind (WB), an organization for dragon conservation and management. Their mission is to protect and manage the dragons within London on behalf of the people.

playlists.title: The Price of Smiles [English Sub]
playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
In a planet far, far away from Earth, there reigns a kingdom that overflows with smiles.
Princess Yuki is 12 years old and is beginning to feel the roller coaster of emotions that come with adolescence. Each day is a mixture of tears, laughter, and dare we say giddiness. Yet the palace is full of fun, with vassals who add color to her life. There's Laila the tutor, Izana the political advisor, Harold the Grand Master, and of course Joshua, a childhood friend and close aide.

"Yuki! As long as you have the will and passion, you can do anything!" says Joshua.
"Ugh. That again?! Joshua, you need to act more regal!" she replies.

Seventeen-year-old Stella is a brilliant warrior. Even though she is cool as a cucumber, she never fails to smile. That's because smiling is essential to life.

This is a story about two girls born in a distant planet.

playlists.title: 笑容的代价 [中字]
playlists.description: 在地球遥远彼端的星球上，有一个洋溢着笑容的王国。十二岁的公主优姬，正步入多愁善感的年纪。她一边过着有哭有笑，时而怦然心动…？的每一天，一边快乐地在王宫中生活着。忠实的家臣们为她的生活点缀了色彩。负责教育的蕾拉、辅佐政治的伊萨那、骑士团长哈路德，以及…身为侍从的儿时玩伴约书亚。“优姬！只要有气势和毅力，不管什么事都能办到！”“……真是的。又在说这个了～！？约书亚，你应该要更有贵族的样子才对！”十七岁的史黛拉，是个能干又冷静的军人。然而她却无时无刻面带微笑…。因为为了要活下去，笑容是不可或缺的。这是诞生在遥远的星球上的，两个少女的故事。

playlists.title: The Ryuo's Work Is Never Done! [English Sub]
playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
I opened the door, and there was a little girl standing there...

“As promised, I’ve come to be your student!”
Yaichi Kuzuryu has become the “Ryuo”, the highest title in Shogi, at the age of 16, only to find Ai Hinatsuru, a 9 year old girl in the third grade, standing outside his door.

“Huh? My student?”
“You don’t remember?”

He didn’t, but he ended up living with this elementary school anyway. Her straightforward passion began to restore something in his heart that he’d almost lost.

playlists.title: 龙王的工作！ [中字]
playlists.description:
一打开玄关大门，有个国小女生就在那里——
“我按照约定，来请您收我为徒了！”
九头龙八一年仅十六岁就拿下将棋界最强大的“龙王”头衔，而他家里却出现一位国小三年级学生，雏鹤爱，九岁。
“呃？……收你为徒？什么？”
“……您不记得了吗？”
八一完全不记得自己答应过的事，却展开了与JS同居的生活。雏鹤爱坦率又热烈的情感，让他慢慢恢复了逐渐丧失的热情。

playlists.description:
天才魔法律家．六冰透（六冰）和他的助手．草野次郎（郎次）回来啦～～！
出现在名拍档．六冰与郎次眼前的大人物，正是于全国内坐拥９９间分部的魔法律事务所．五岭集团的总帅．五岭陀罗尼丸及五岭的助手．惠比寿花夫。
两边阵营赌上身为魔法律专家的自尊进行较量，分出胜负之时，六冰与郎次之间竟产生了不可磨灭的分歧！
两人各自面对阻挡在自己眼前的试炼，为了再度成为最强拍档而努力！

playlists.title: 高校之神 [中字]
playlists.description:
自称最强的高中生“陈．毛利”。
在收到了一个为了决定最强高中生的大会“高校之神”的邀请后，他的人生彻底改变了。
只要能够获得冠军，就能实现任何的愿望……
心中怀抱着各种不同愿望的强敌们一一现身，
而在这场战斗的尽头等待着他们的究竟又是什么呢？
在一群不简单的高中生之间，一场不可理喻的战斗正式开幕！！

Mori Jin has proclaimed himself the strongest high schooler. 
His life changes when he's invited to participate in ""God of High School,"" a tournament to determine the strongest high schooler of all. 
He's told that if he wins, any wish he makes will be granted... 
All the participants are powerful contenders who fight their hardest for their own wishes. 
What awaits them at the end of the tournament? 
A chaotic battle between unbelievably strong high school students is about to begin!

playlists.title: 非枪人生 第2季 [中字]
playlists.description: “身体机能扩张技术”是贝鲁联公司在战争期间开发的新技术。透过该技术使得部分身体、甚至整个身体都机械化的人们则被称为“扩张者”。扩张者与身为普通人类的非扩张者在社会中共同生活，也因此使得纷争不曾间断。干十三则是做着“处理屋”的工作，靠解决这些问题维生。而十三本人，亦是个头部是巨大手枪的“扩张者”。有一天，一个全身扩张者的壮汉找上了十三，并委托他保护一位少年。这位少年的名字叫荒吐铁朗，是壮汉从贝鲁联公司手中诱拐来的少年。十三虽然接下了委托，但铁朗却被贝鲁联公司派来的追兵夺走了。于是十三便在不知不觉中与在城市之中执牛耳地位的贝鲁联公司扯上了关系。诱拐铁朗的全身扩张者男子究竟何方神圣？而贝鲁联公司与铁朗之间又有什么关系？

playlists.title: 哥布林杀手 [中字]
playlists.description:
“我不拯救世界，只管杀哥布林”

据说，在这间边境公会中，有个只靠讨伐哥布林就升上银等（第三位阶）的稀有存在…一名女神官成为冒险者后，首次组成队伍出征，就在冒险中陷入了危机。而拯救了她的，正是那名被称为“哥布林杀手”的男人。

他不择手段、不惜劳苦，仅为消灭哥布林。女神官被这样的他所摆布、公会柜台小姐对他心怀感激、青梅竹马的养牛妹等待着他。一名森人（Elf）少女听闻他的事迹后，也现身委托任务……。

playlists.title: Goblin Slayer [English Sub]
playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
"I'm not going to save the world. I'm just going to kill goblins."

In a guild on the frontier, there existed someone rare—who rose to a silver-ranked adventurer just by hunting goblins.

A priestess, a newly minted adventurer, joins her first party only to find themselves in a pinch. The one who saved them, was none other than the man who was known as the Goblin Slayer.

Using all means necessary and sparing no effort, he only eliminates goblins. The priestess who ends up dragged around by him, the Guild receptionist who’s indebted to him, and his cattle-ranching childhood friend who waits for him. And upon hearing rumours about him, an elven girl appears with a request…

The story is set in Mamuceaster, where shiny sand and its crystal shiny stone are used to run the city. The girls who practice magic by spells and melodies via shiny sand and shiny stone are known as a “Witch”. With singing and defeating monsters, they are longed by crowds and giving hopes to everyone.

Flora Girls Academy, founded by the Witch of the Dawn, is a school for training witches. 
In the hope to become a great witch, Tiara arrives at the academy.

“Please allow me to enroll in this academy … huh!?”

故事发生于普遍使用"辉砂"以及其结晶体"辉石"作为动力的城市．玛姆盖斯提尔。

运用辉砂与辉石、以咒语或旋律来发动魔法的少女被称为"魔女"，进行着歌唱活动以及驱除怪兽，被人们所敬仰着。

晓之魔女所创设，齐聚了见习魔女们的学校．芙萝拉女子学院。
梦想成为出色魔女的少女．缇亚拉来到了这所学院的门前。

playlists.description:
简体中文字幕播放清单: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLwLSw1_eDZl2kRY8vEPyAWNhsDilEGeyc

＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
Welcome to the town of Lindworm, where humans and monsters coexist and rookie doctor Glenn carries out some…risqué medical examinations!

Whether probing deep into the gills of a mermaid,
suturing the thigh of a flesh golem,
helping a harpy lay an egg,
or palpating each and every scale of a dragon…

No matter how different their looks, bodies, and properties, Glenn devotes his all to saving them—and, in the process, winds up in some pretty dangerous liaisons…? But don’t worry—it’s all just a part of his medical exams! 

Thus Glenn kicks off another day at the office, even as his lamia assistant Sapphee is about to wrap her tail around his neck!

It’s the world’s first medical fantasy that takes a deep dive into the lives and anatomy of monster girls!

playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
Saitama is a hero who only became a hero for fun. After three years of “special” training, though, he’s become so strong that he’s practically invincible. In fact, he’s too strong—even his mightiest opponents are taken out with a single punch, and it turns out that being devastatingly powerful is actually kind of a bore. 
With his passion for being a hero lost along with his hair, yet still faced with new enemies every day, how much longer can he keep it going?

playlists.title: [MalaySub] A3!
playlists.description:
“Puan Pengarah, tolong bantu kami berkembang!”
Di Tokyo, terdapat tempat yang bernama Laluan Velude. Daerah yang dipenuhi dengan persembahan serta kumpulan pementasan berbakat. Izumi Tachibana merupakan bekas pelakon pentas, menerima surat menyatakan “Penuh dengan hutang! Tiada pelanggan! Cuma satu pelakon saja!” Itu menjelaskan situasi yang dihadapi oleh kumpulan pementasan yang terkenal dahulu, Syarikat Mankai. Tugasnya adalah mengembalikan zaman kegemilangan dengan menjadi pemilik baharu serta pengarah kepada kumpulan tersebut

playlists.title: [MalaySub] ARGONAVIS from BanG Dream!
playlists.description:
Ren Nanahoshi merupakan pelajar kolej yang tidak begitu mahir berkomunikasi bersama orang lain. Dia masih merasakan debaran dalam hatinya apabila melihat persembahan langsung kumpulan muzik sewaktu dia kecil lalu meluangkan masa keseharian mencari identiti dirinya.
Satu hari kemudian, seorang remaja bernama Yuuto dan Wataru melihat bakat menyanyi Ren semasa dia berkaraoke seorang diri. Mereka berdua mengatakan: “Inilah takdir. Mari tubuhkan kugiran!” Ren terus melarikan diri namun takdir telah mula melangkah begitu jugalah pengembaraan mereka bersama.

playlists.title: [MalaySub] Diary of our Days at the Breakwater
playlists.description: Hina Tsurugi, yang baru berpindah dari bandar ke luar bandar. Dia lebih suka buat kerja di dalam rumah dan geli pada haiwan. Dia bercadang nak masuk ke dalam kelab kraf tangan dan nikmati hari-hari persekolahan. Namun, ketika dia berjumpa Yuki Kuroiwa ketika bersiar-siar, dia telah masuk ke dalam sebuah kelab yang bernama "Kelab Tetobu". Di kelab itu, dia mula memancing. Apa yang akan terjadi pada kehidupan sekolah Hina ketika di sekeliling oleh kawan-kawan yang pelik?

playlists.title: [MalaySub] ARTE
playlists.description: Pada abad ke-16 di Florence. Arte dilahirkan sebagai anak perempuan bangsawan. Namun beliau tertarik dengan bidang seni dan ukiran patung di sekelilingnya sejak dari kecil lagi. Impiannya adalah untuk menjadi seorang pelukis sendiri, tetapi pada masa ini dia tidak dapat menerima bahawa wanita tidak boleh menjadi pelukis tambahan pula daripada golongan bangsawan. Hal ini telah mendesak Arte dengan membuat keputusannya untuk menyahut cabaran untuk mencapai impian hidupnya.

playlists.title: [MalaySub] Ascendance of a Bookworm S1+S2
playlists.description:
Menjadi Penjaga Kuil buku!
Seorang pustakawan yang gemarkan buku, Urano Motosu mati dalam sebuah kemalangan yang tak disangka. Bila dia sedar, Urano telah dihidupkan semula sebagai seorang anak perempuan kepada askar, bernama Myne.
Di dunia itu bangsawan ada kuasa magis dan jarang rakyat biasa lahir dengan kuasa magis. Mereka tak boleh selamat tanpa ada alat magis yang menyerab kuasa yang ada tanpa had tersebut.
Pada masa itu, Myne menjumpai sebuah kuil pustakawan di upacara keagamaan dan meminta pada ketua paderi itu untuk menjadi perintis menjaga kuil itu. Selepas itu, Myne dilantik sebagai Perintis Biru bagi menjaga kuil itu.
Namun, tak semua sanggup menggunakan jubah biru itu yang telah diberikan oleh bangsawan bagi menjaga tempat tersebut. Myne menghadapi kesukaran di dalam perjalannya.

playlists.title: [MalaySub] Shachibato! President, It's Time for Battle
playlists.description:
Pusat dunia, Gate Pier...
Dulu dunia ini cuma alam magik yang bertanah tandus tanpa penghujung.
Seorang dewi turun dari langit dan “Gerbang” yang gergasi muncul di langit.
Orang ramai mendapat tahu tentang kewujudan tenaga ajaib yang mampu menampung dunia ini iaitu Kirakuri. Berlalunya hari dan bulan, Gate Pier membangun menjadi sebuah Bandar.
Pemburu harta karun yang mengkhusu dalam pengumpulan Kirakuri di dalam “Gerbang” mula muncul.  Tenaga ajaib yang menampung dunia diamanah kepada Pemburu Kirakuri.
Pada suatu hari, watak utama Minato tiba-tiba diseru oleh kawan semenjak kecil dia, Yutoria.
Dengan harapan yang kecil, Minato menuju ke tempat itu lalu diluahkan perasaan oleh Yutoria…
“Aku rasa… Kau sesuai menjadi seorang presiden!”
Dengan itu Minato mewarisi ayah dia dan kehidupan dia sebagai Presiden Pengembar bermula.

playlists.title: [MalaySub] Shironeko Project
playlists.description:
Pada zaman dulu, di langit ada Kerajaan Putih dan di tanah Kerajaan Hitam.
Mereka saling melindungi “keseimbangan” sambil meneruskan “kitaran hidup”.

Pada suatu hari, seorang pemuda menggali kubur di kampong yang dibinasakan olh raksasa Kerajaan Hitam. Skears, calon Raja Kegelapan sebelum ini tiba di tempat pemuda itu.
Pemuda yang dijumpai oleh Skears, berazam untuk menjadi Putera Kegelapan demi menukar dunia ini.

Sementara itu, Iris, Raja Cahaya yang merupakan Dewi Pelindung Kerajaan Putih,
merasa bimbang kerana “keseimbangan”  akan dirosakkan.

Berita mengenai kemunculan Bal yang mengacau keseimbangan dalam datang.
Raja Kegelapan dari Kerajaan Hitam datang memohon untuk bekerjasama demi menghapuskan Bal yang menyakitkan hati dia.

Raja Cahaya, Iris telah bertemu dengan Putera Pengutus Hitam,
lalu mereka berdu pun berjanji untuk bersama-sama membawakan keamanan kepada dunia.

Namun janji antara mereka berdua akan dirosakkan oleh Raja Kegelapan.

Janji antara mereka berdua dan dosa permulaan iaitu menghancurkan dunia.
Kisah menuju ke akar umbi Zero bakal membuka tirai…

playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
Hina Tsurugi just moved from the city to rural area. She's an indoor girl and doesn't like dealing with living things.

Hina planned on joining in the handcraft club and enjoy her school life there, but one day she met Yuki Kuroiwa during a walk. She was then made to join a strange "Breakwater Club" and started fishing. Surrounded by club members with different presonalities, what will Hina's high school life become?

playlists.title: Shironeko Project ZERO CHRONICLE [English Sub]
playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
A long, long time ago... the Kingdom of White that existed in the sky, and the Kingdom of Black on earth, circulated in equilibrium.

At one point in the Kingdom of Black, a young man was digging a tomb in a village that was destroyed by demons.  A former candidate to the throne - Skiers - appears before the young man. He, who was found by Skiers, decides that he will change the world by becoming the Prince of Darkness.

On the other hand, the guardian goddess, the King of the Kingdom of White, Iris, is worried that the balance between light and darkness will be broken.

The existence that threatens to unhinge this balance - Ba'al - appears. 

The King of Darkness, of the Kingdom of Darkness, offers up a pledge to defeat Ba'al.

The King of Light meets with the Prince of Darkness, who acts as a messenger from the Kingdom of Darkness, and they ＜Promise＞ to work to bring about a peaceful world together.

However, this promise was trampled on by the King of Darkness. 
The ＜Promise＞ between the two, and the sin of destroying the world. 

This is the beginning of a story that leads to the source of everything!

playlists.title: 白猫计划 零之纪元 [中字]
playlists.description:
从前从前，天空有着白之王国，地上有着黑暗王国。
两个王国保持〈均衡〉的同时不断〈循环〉着。

某天，有名少年在黑暗王国中某个被魔兽摧毁的村庄里挖着坟墓。
此时，前任黑暗之王的继任者“史奇亚兹”出现在那名少年面前。
被“史奇亚兹”看上的少年就这样成了闇之王子，并下定决心要改变这个世界。

另一方面，白之王国的守护神──光明之王“爱莉丝”则在担心光与闇的均衡被打破一事。

就在这时，传来扰乱均衡的存在“巴尔”现身的消息。
黑暗王国的黑暗之王为了讨伐碍眼的“巴尔”，向白之王国提出了结盟的邀请。

光明之王艾莉丝与作为使者从黑暗王国前来的闇之王子会面，
并缔结了要一同创造和平世界的〈约定〉。

然而，黑暗之王却破坏了两人所交换的〈约定〉。

两人的〈约定〉以及毁灭世界原罪。
通往〈根源〉(零)的故事就此展开——

playlists.title: Shachibato! President, It's Time for Battle! [English Sub]
playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝ 
The heart of the world - Gatopia. Formerly, the world was a wasteland that continued to be so for ages... 

Then, at one point, a goddess descended from the sky, and a giant gate materialised. People who went into the Gates found Sparkling Crystals, the mysterious energy that has been sustaining the world. Time goes by, and Gatopia started developing as a city. Some people started collecting Sparkling Crystals in dungeons as a professional job, and they are called "treasure hunters". The mysterious energy that is sustaining the world, is now into the hands of Sparkling Crystal hunters.

One day, our MC Minato was suddenly called out by his childhood friend Yutoria. He came to meet her while kind of expecting a confession, only to be told that… “I've always thought that you're suited to become the president of a company!” 

And that's how he succeeded his family business and started his life of adventure.

playlists.title: 社长，战斗的时间到了 [中字]
playlists.description:
这次的“异世界”，是不同于以往的职场

世界的中心，盖特比亚。
曾经，世界是一望无际的荒野、无边的魔境。
但是女神从天而降、巨大的“门”随之出现于空中。
人们发现“门”中存在能维持世界的奇迹能量──光水晶

时光飞逝，盖特比亚发展成了大都市。
众多专门采集光水晶的宝藏猎人日以继夜地探索“门”内的迷宫。
能维持世界的奇迹能量，就这样交付到光水晶猎人的手中。

主角・凑有一天突然受青梅竹马・尤托莉亚邀约。
凑抱着一丝期待赴约，
而尤托莉亚却对凑说──
“我觉得你……很适合当社长呢！”。
就这样继承了前任社长的脚步，凑开始了他的冒险社长生活。

playlists.title: Ascendance of a Bookworm S2 [English Sub]
playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
I’ll become a temple maiden for the sake of books!

Motosu Urano, a college girl who loves books even more than her three meals a day, was reincarnated as a soldier’s daughter named Maine, into a world where there are no books. There was a low literacy rate among commoners, and books made of parchment were expensive and belonged only to the nobles.

And so, Maine made a decision—“If there are no books, then I’ll just have to make them!”

After much trial and error, Maine met the merchant Benno, and in order to become a merchant apprentice, completed the plant-based paper. However, Maine’s body was getting eroded by the “Fever of the Devouring…”

In this world where the nobles possess magical powers, ordinary citizens are sometimes born with magic. This is known as the “Devouring”. Without magical items to absorb the ever-increasing magical power, one will not be able to live for long. 

Then, Maine, who discovered the temple’s library during the baptism, made a direct request to become an apprentice temple maiden to the bishop. After much ado, it was decided that Maine would become a blue-robed apprentice temple maiden who would devote her magic to the temple.

However, there were many who were unhappy with Maine, of commoner birth, for wearing the blue robes that were originally meant for nobility. Maine faces a difficult path.

Her problematic servants, and the hierarchical society of the temple…

The common sense and practices of the temple that differed from that of when she was Urano, and even from the neighbourhood where she lived, stands in Maine’s way.

Will the day come when Maine can read as much as she wants!?
And, will Maine ever be able to make a book!?

playlists.title: ARTE [English Sub]
playlists.description:
＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
The stage is set in early 16th century Florence, Italy.  The birthplace of the arts in the Renaissance period, painting, sculpting and the like thrived. Arte, a young lady born into nobility in an era with such blossoming energy, became absorbed into the art of painting the moment she became aware. However, in an age where the concept of an ""independent woman"" did not exist, girls were not allowed to even pursue their hobbies. In defiance of her mother's wishes for her to be wedded and live a proper life, Arte looks for an Atelier willing to take her in as a painter's apprentice. If she is going to have regrets anyway, she will do it on her own terms!

Struggling against current trends, a young lady on the path to become a professional painter, here begins Arte's story.

playlists.description:
故事的舞台是16世纪初的义大利・佛罗伦斯。
绘画与雕刻等艺术盛行的文艺复兴发祥地。
在这样一个充满朝气和华丽的时代，出身贵族的阿尔蒂自从懂事以来就对绘画着迷不已。
然而在这个不谅解女性追求独立的时代，她们不被允许做自己喜欢的事。
阿尔蒂反抗母亲希望她结婚过体面日子的期待，为了成为画家，自愿成为工作坊的弟子。
既然都会感到后悔，宁愿做过自己想做的事后再后悔。
对抗时代潮流，选择走上画家之路的少女，阿尔蒂的故事即将展开。

playlists.title: 宝石商理察的谜鉴定 [中字]
playlists.description:
正义感强大的大学生．中田正义
某个夜晚，帮助了被醉汉缠上的美丽外国人．理察

得知了对方是一位宝石商，
正义将祖母直到去世都带着的，有着隐情的戒指委托给他鉴定。
经由理察的鉴定中明朗化的，是祖母的过去、真实、以及想念。

以此为契机，正义开始在理察担任店主的银座宝石店【Jewelry etranger】打工。

理察和正义间的关系，
随着解开各式各样被带进etranger的“谜题”
也逐渐产生变化，

然而两人，
却有着各自没有对他人明言的秘密——

playlists.description:
位于东京郊外，有座天鹅绒镇。镇上有条伫立了许多剧团，被称之为“天鹅绒之路”的道路，是剧团演员们的圣地。
而立花泉，受一封信所托，来到了位于天鹅绒之路的“MANKAI剧团”。那是她父亲立花幸夫曾经建立的剧团。但是父亲本人却从八年前开始便杳无音讯，加上没有观众，剧团负债，演员甚至只有一人。泉为了重整陷入危机的剧团，作为团长以及总监督开始四处奔波。
究竟，“MANKAI剧团”的命运会如何前进呢——

＝＝＝＝Title Summary＝＝＝＝
On the outskirts of Tokyo lies a street known as "Velude Way", the sacred street where many theatres call home. Armed with only a letter, Tachibana Izumi visits the Mankai Company, a troupe theater company that was founded by her father.

Now theater is deserted and there has been no news of her father since 8 years ago. Without an audience, and only a single member in the troupe, the debtors are at the door. 

Can Izumi somehow revive the former troupe? Where will fate lead Mankai Company?

playlists.title: 怕痛的我，把防御力点满就对了 [中字]
playlists.description:
“大受欢迎的VRMMO“NewWorld Online”出现了超强新人！？”

能让所有攻击失效，以致死毒的技能彻底蹂躏怪物和玩家！
那不寻常的战斗英姿，被称之为“移动要塞”或“最终魔王”。
而那位玩家的真面目，居然仅仅是一名菜鸟美少女！
 
想要隐瞒什么的梅普露，
在朋友莎莉的推荐下，刚刚开始玩游戏。
缺乏游戏常识的她，把属性点点在防御力上点满了，
尽管一开始被小喽啰怪物耍得团团转，然而……。
 
不……痛！？
 
即使被怪物拳打脚踢也毫无损伤，
更走运的是，还得到了一击必杀的反击技能！
非比寻常的同伴们加入，梅普露也渐渐变强。
毫发无伤的大冒险，正式拉开序幕！

There's a super strong newbie in the world of the VRMMO "NewWorld Online"!? 

The one who can render all attacks useless, and completely crush all monsters and users with a "Lethal Poison" skill! 

The one with an unusual one of a kind fighting posture, termed as the "Moving Fortress", or the "Final Demon King". 

And the true face behind this player, is none other a newbie Bishoujo! 

Maple, by recommendation from Sally, starts playing NewWorld Online. But being completely new to the game, she allocates all of her ability points into her defense power (VIT). 

And though these little pesky monsters are really annoying but…

It… doesn't hurt!? 

Getting plummeled by monster and yet completely unscathed.. And what's even luckier is being able to acquire the ultimate counter attack skill! 

With an unusual ally joining the team, Maple gradually gets stronger. The adventure (without any damage) , is about to begin!

playlists.title: 吸血鬼仆人剧场版 - Alice in the Garden [中字]
playlists.description: 椿消失无踪，所有人都回到安稳的日常生活。但好景不常，突然之间城市里下起了不合时节的的雪。真昼认为这异常的气候或许和吸血鬼有所关连，决定召集所有的主人，并且也联络了”色欲”的主人-有栖院御园。然而御园却表示自己现在不方便行动，晚点再跟大家会合。难得看到御园有口难言的模样，而之后他却这样断了音讯。就在此时，御园的哥哥御国出现在担心御园安危的大家面前。有栖院家刻意隐瞒的与”色欲”和”嫉妒”有关的过去。御园被封印的记忆，即将被解开。

playlists.title: 如果有妹妹就好了。 [中字]
playlists.description:
只要有个妹妹的话
我的人生就永远处在巅峰的说，
为什么我没有妹妹呢…..

只写关于妹妹题材的妹控小说家˙羽岛伊月的身边围绕着，明明是天才作家却十足变态的可儿那由多、女大学生白川京、插画家屁桃、鬼畜税金救星大野艾希莉等个性丰富的人物。
伊月他们虽然各有各的烦恼，但依旧过着小说照写，游戏照玩，酒照喝，税照报的热闹生活。而默默温暖在旁守护他们的伊月家没有血缘关系的弟弟千寻，其实隐藏着某个天大的秘密。
开心却带着心酸的天才与凡人与变态所展开的青春爱情搞笑群像剧，揭幕了！

Every day is full of fun. But something is missing. "My life would be amazing if only I had a little sister. Why don’t I have a little sister...?" These are the musings of little sister-lover and novelist Itsuki Hashima, who only writes works featuring little sisters. Around him gather a number of unique people: genius author/pervert Nayuta, female college student Miyako, illustrator Puriketsu, and the brutish tax accountant Ashley. Each of them hold their own worries, but live their peaceful daily lives while writing novels, playing video games, drinking alcohol, and filing their tax returns.

playlists.title: 枪弹辩驳3未来编 & 绝望编 [中字]
playlists.description:
未来编--大纲
“超高校级的绝望”所引发的“人类史上最大最恶的绝望事件”，使得过去的世界被逼入崩坏的绝境。为了拯救这充满绝望的世界，有人设立了“未来机关”。打倒江之岛盾子的苗木诚等第78届生也加入了未来机关。他们虽然为了复兴世界而持续进行着活动，但苗木却因为曾包庇“绝望的余党”而被指控犯下了叛逆罪。未来机关的成员们为了决定苗木的处份而齐聚一堂，但他们却遭到了黑白熊的监禁，并且被迫展开了“最后的互相残杀”。他们的手腕上被装上了奇怪的手环，每经过一定时间就会被施打安眠药。接着，成员中混入了会杀死未来机关成员的背叛者。“想要活下去就只能找出背叛者并加以杀害”，没有学级审判规则的互相残杀。要杀人或者是被杀，苗木等人被逼入了这场极限状态的死亡游戏中。希望将希望杀死的，绝望的故事即将开始。


绝望编--大纲
以集结各大领域的超一流高中生并加以培育为目的所设立，政府公认特权级学园“私立希望峰学园”。这间学园设有聚集了拥有“超高校级才能”的“本科”，以及只要缴交高额学费谁都可以入学的“预备学科”。本科的“第77届生”们不只充满了才能，连性格也都相当有个性。但是他们并不只执着于自己的才能，他们认为人生最重要的并非是才能，而是透过与人们的接触琢磨自己的人格、创造回忆，他们各自过着如同普通高中生般的校园生活。但在台面下，却有一项神秘的计划在进行，同时学园学科差别问题也在横行着。然后，渴望才能的预备学科少年．日向创。发生在他身上的命运般的相遇，将会把学园以及未来导向无法预测的方向。这是人类史上最大最恶的绝望事件以前的故事。以绝望收场的、希望的故事。

playlists.title: DANGANRONPA The Animation [English Sub]
playlists.description:
The Hope's Peak Academy promises success in life just by graduating. However, only a very limited number of people are allowed to enter this school. Only students with outstanding talents, known as the "ultimates", were allowed to enter.

And now, a boy is about to set foot in this school. The protagonist, Makoto Naegi, is an ordinary boy with no special characteristics. He is the only one who was allowed to enter the academy by lottery, and he is the only one with Ultimate Lucky Student. Naegi cannot hide his excitement at his good fortune and new environment. But what awaits him is a situation he never imagined.

A shock runs through his body as soon as he sets foot inside the school gates. The next time Makoto wakes up, he finds himself locked in a sealed school building with 14 other students.

Furthermore, Monokuma, who calls himself the headmaster, appeared in front of Naegi and his friends, who were puzzled by the sudden situation. He tells them. From now on, they will live here for the rest of their lives. If they want to graduate from the academy, they must kill their fellow students.

playlists.title: 非枪人生NO GUNS LIFE [中字]
playlists.description: “身体机能扩张技术”是贝鲁联公司在战争期间开发的新技术。透过该技术使得部分身体、甚至整个身体都机械化的人们则被称为“扩张者”。扩张者与身为普通人类的非扩张者在社会中共同生活，也因此使得纷争不曾间断。干十三则是做着“处理屋”的工作，靠解决这些问题维生。而十三本人，亦是个头部是巨大手枪的“扩张者”。有一天，一个全身扩张者的壮汉找上了十三，并委托他保护一位少年。这位少年的名字叫荒吐铁朗，是壮汉从贝鲁联公司手中诱拐来的少年。十三虽然接下了委托，但铁朗却被贝鲁联公司派来的追兵夺走了。于是十三便在不知不觉中与在城市之中执牛耳地位的贝鲁联公司扯上了关系。诱拐铁朗的全身扩张者男子究竟何方神圣？而贝鲁联公司与铁朗之间又有什么关系？

playlists.title: 警视厅 特务部 特殊凶恶犯对策室 第七课 [中字]
playlists.description:
只是纯粹的追寻着憧憬之物──

远古时代。

这个世界上存在着精灵、矮人、吸血鬼、人造人、人类等等各式各样的种族。
君临纷争不息的生存金字塔顶端的，曾是『龙族』。

经过漫长的时光，龙族消逝，馀下的种族都选择了共存的生活方式。随着时代更迭，各个种族除却些微外表上的特徵，几乎演化成为与人类无异的
样貌。

2X19年，东京。

即便是看似平稳的现代社会，犯罪行为依然不曾消失。现代出现了一个醉心于过往『龙族』威势、企图掌握其力量而不惜行凶的组织
──『NINE』。该组织屡次策画凶恶犯罪，企图颠覆重组现今世界的构成。

为了与『NINE』相抗衡，警视厅从各个部属聚集了精英组成对策部门。其名为『警视厅　特务部　特殊凶恶犯罪对策室　第七课　－－通称特七』。 传言中成员虽然各个身怀绝技、能力出众，却被称为「特立独行集团」、「不成材集团」。

以新人之姿加入这样的特七的主角．七月清司。
在被性格迥异的成员们耍弄得团团转之际，依然用天生的开朗率直个性面对，一肩挑起解决NINE事件的重责大任。

在接二连三发生的难解事件之中，他是否能找到自己相信的正义价值──。

= TITLE SUMMARY =

Long ago...

Many different races inhabited the Earth alongside humans - elves, dwarves, vampires, homunculi, and more...

At the top of this endless power hierarchy, were dragons. However, a long time passed and dragons simply disappeared. The remaining races chose to live in co-existence. As time passed, everyone began to look like humans.

2X19, Tokyo.

This was thought of as a peaceful era. However, crimes never ceased to occur. In adoration of the dragons of old, a criminal organization - Nine - carried out excessively horrible crimes in search of the dragon’s power. Their plan is to commit horrible crimes and change the current world.

To oppose Nine, a special resistance team made up of experts was created by the police department. Nicknamed ‘Tokunana’, this team is made up of highly qualified individuals that stand above their peers. At the same time, they are rumoured to be a group of strays and good-for-nothings. Then one day, a new member Seiji Nanatsuki is assigned to the unit. While being constantly teased and messed with by the members of the unit, Seiji continues to tackle cases with his inherent brightness and straightforwardness. Can he find the justice that he believes in as he continues to handle difficult cases?

playlists.title: 入间同学入魔了 [中字]
playlists.description:
欢迎来到充满欢笑的魔界！！

受人请託总是无法拒绝的烂好人少年．铃木入间因为一段奇妙的机缘而成为了魔界的大恶魔．萨利班的孙子！
备受溺爱的入间，进入了萨利班担任理事长的恶魔学校就读…。

儘管入间隐瞒自己的人类身份、希望能渡过一段和平的校园生活，但他不知为何总是备受注目。
不但有恶魔菁英跑来找他打架、有珍兽系（？）女子喜欢接近他，甚至还被严格的学生会长给盯上了！

面对接踵而来的麻烦，入间将利用他与生俱来的温柔个性逐一克服难关！

= Episode Summary =

Welcome to a laughter-filled Demon World!

Iruma Suzuki is a good-natured young man who cannot turn down any request. One day, through a miraculous turn of fate, he becomes the grandson of the king of hell, Sullivan. The well-loved Iruma starts to attend the demon academy where Sullivan is the head of the board.

While hiding the fact that he is a human, Iruma-kun wishes to live a peaceful school life, but for some reason, he’s always the center of attention.

Elite demons pick fights with him, rare demon-girls are attracted to him, and Iruma-kun even finds himself in the crosshairs of the strict student council president. As he encounters each problem, Iruma-kun overcomes it with his inherent kindness!

playlists.description:
没错，我觉醒了！
 
高中生圣瑞姬由于个人因素在不上不下的时期转学到皆神高中。

命中注定在那裡邂逅了一群中二病不断加剧的遗憾系男子――「英雄社」。
瑞姬不知怎的被捲入英雄社的活动，
他们无时无刻展开的妄想和失控耍得瑞姬团团转，
可以说已经来不及吐嘈了！连心累的时间都没有了！
 
「……怪了。我期望的明明是安稳的高中生活……！」
期望拥有安稳高中生活的瑞姬和中二病男子们所交织出，妄想爆发的中二病鸡飞狗跳校园喜剧，正式开幕☆
